<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no" ?>
<FinalDraft DocumentType="Script" Template="No" Version="6">

  <DocumentRef DateTime="20260328T023500" id="75b0038b-1dcf-46b2-b38a-896d2895c1c3">
    <XRef DateTime="20250719T224917" id="326d3bbb-277d-4966-b8b4-fc0c38660087"/>
    <XRef DateTime="20250719T225100" id="311bf653-30ed-4d65-a49b-1d9bc7012bab"/>
  </DocumentRef>

  <Content>
    <Paragraph Type="New Act" id="6b67055e-8e0a-4c01-b26e-48bdef828a9a">
      <Text>Cold Open</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading" id="f8e26f32-71ab-4cd7-b50d-e493d06a3ec6">
      <SceneProperties Length="1 6/8" Page="1" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="CLAY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="KIDS">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RAY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="ROCKET">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="STARDUST">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text Style="Bold+AllCaps">Ext. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Style="Bold+AllCaps">Miniverse</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="49223ad7-68ea-4b39-873b-a0dae5ec67b7">
      <Text>The world is framed in a 4:3 aspect ratio. A decorative </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">pop-up book</Text>
      <Text> titled </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">Stardust </Text>
      <Text>cracks open. A ROCKET SHIP with a friendly, animated face pops out from the pages.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="c45f4abb-a0be-4f04-86aa-c562447efe90">
      <Text Style="AllCaps">Clay</Text>
      <Text> (24), radiating energy in a colorful cosmic vest, appears in the rocket’s window and waves enthusiastically.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="570a04a0-92a2-4143-ac11-5dff94016394">
      <Text>ClAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="459eb441-6eeb-4e12-b6bb-29086e10f115">
      <Text>Planets, comets, and galaxies everywhere! It’s me, Clay! Have you seen our best friend, Stardust?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="eeb237ab-df23-478f-b40a-69b2f90d3f09">
      <Text Style="AllCaps">Stardust</Text>
      <Text>, an animated, whimsical mudpuppy, soars out from behind a cardboard star and loops around the ship.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="c68e5431-9051-4285-8437-7e5009cbbe94">
      <Text>Stardust</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="af782bb0-7bd6-4705-b26b-fb6a7ea6d1f5">
      <Text>Twinkle, twinkle, twinkle!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="fbf10ab5-16ce-4999-9bf6-bbeb3956e437">
      <Text>Unseen </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">kids</Text>
      <Text> answer in unison along with </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">Trini</Text>
      <Text Size="10"> </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">“Ray”</Text>
      <Text Size="10"> </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">Reyes</Text>
      <Text Size="10"> </Text>
      <Text>(4).</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="General" id="f2ec3210-f2bb-431c-b685-027d79f3fee4">
      <DualDialogue>
        <SpellCheckIgnoreLists>
          <IgnoredRanges/>
          <IgnoredWords/>
        </SpellCheckIgnoreLists>
        <Paragraph Type="Character" id="8046f8c3-c582-4d98-94ba-2b6f0788680c">
          <Text>Kids (V.O.)</Text>
        </Paragraph>
        <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="bd419307-8c3a-495d-8d23-47fe1d94104e">
          <Text>There she is!</Text>
        </Paragraph>
        <Paragraph Type="Character" id="5c292767-b3d1-4895-ad7b-08beb9253101">
          <Text>Ray (V.O.)</Text>
        </Paragraph>
        <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="a6eb9f70-ebda-4bee-bfd8-d3c965e23a5d">
          <Text>She’s right behind you!</Text>
        </Paragraph>
      </DualDialogue>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="306c14ec-fd57-4917-b334-0b00fa3f9853">
      <Text>Clay ducks back inside.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="c7e30fa4-19fb-4176-b23c-1f541976e9cb">
      <Text>Rocket</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="7f69c111-1f12-43bb-9a7b-01821c8dced8">
      <Text>Come on in, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">stardusters</Text>
      <Text>!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="0a48a32b-7286-4758-b434-a9918d9bbf6c">
      <Text>The camera follows Stardust as she dives through the window. Inside, the ship is filled with charming cardboard controls.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="c24b2bc2-647e-4a6c-8b50-feb30797a913">
      <Text>ClAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="b4025e30-8c2f-4767-b3fb-b2b1d867636e">
      <Text>Hi! We're so glad you're here! We’re almost ready to land. Stardust? Stardust?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="edc1f33b-684c-4d29-ba4a-a3312d19cc73">
      <Text>Clay searches the cabin. Stardust giggles and ducks underneath a nearby table. Clay turns to the camera.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="3eaac186-a7fc-4177-95ab-4fa6607b04ec">
      <Text>Clay</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="37b17ab6-23ca-47b9-8a00-c2d1e753932d">
      <Text>Did you see Stardust?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="General" id="5192b2c5-ffe0-404c-a8ad-70946faf0ab9">
      <DualDialogue>
        <SpellCheckIgnoreLists>
          <IgnoredRanges/>
          <IgnoredWords/>
        </SpellCheckIgnoreLists>
        <Paragraph Type="Character" id="14f64058-99fd-44e1-bafc-088d0c6cf261">
          <Text>Kids (V.O.)</Text>
        </Paragraph>
        <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="f2486fa3-773e-47da-bc51-f16e6c756269">
          <Text>Right there! Under the table!</Text>
        </Paragraph>
        <Paragraph Type="Character" id="4cb41fbc-f344-4440-8e5c-09fd9555ad94">
          <Text>Ray (V.O.)</Text>
        </Paragraph>
        <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="68dcc84c-7368-418f-96aa-4ec96b20f8c9">
          <Text>Are you blind?!</Text>
        </Paragraph>
      </DualDialogue>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="de9d0760-4b22-437b-8ae0-2cbae3220658">
      <Text>Clay mimics hand-goggles, spotting her with a laugh.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="a1cfd922-cad6-4db0-9edb-4cc136656c0f">
      <Text>ClAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="6c5f6b00-30c8-4b7a-b737-707b6d0b603d">
      <Text>Stardust! What world should we visit today?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="c10cbf10-7f87-4a92-b611-b3bdfc215af6">
      <Text>Clay gestures to the window, where cutouts of a blue, white, and green planet hang against a dark backdrop.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="a02014ad-0594-4204-97d1-c2eaea491eed">
      <Text>Clay</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="17330476-6de2-445b-bba8-1e6967cecf23">
      <Text>A </Text>
      <Text Style="Italic+AllCaps">blue</Text>
      <Text> planet? A </Text>
      <Text Style="Italic+AllCaps">clue</Text>
      <Text> we need bathing suits. Do you have one?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="202ccddf-9c8b-4f86-899a-e93fed6a87b1">
      <Text>Stardust shakes her head no.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="d712f87d-94a0-4049-9db2-56fa0ca06dfe">
      <Text>ClAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="7fcef733-e346-40ba-9c14-859dbd9a5c0a">
      <Text>Should we land on the white planet? </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">Brrr</Text>
      <Text>! Do you have your winter coat?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="8717af61-a8bf-4aac-a3b6-6b50d2f058c9">
      <Text>Stardust shakes her head no. Clay points to the final world.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="334014ba-b16b-43be-b55b-d657d4f1dcc2">
      <Text>Clay</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="1e6b95de-ee4a-4b0c-8d24-ce88a79213e3">
      <Text>Then what color is this one?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="db339cf5-59cd-4e29-99a4-4750b717b48d">
      <Text>KiDS (V.O.)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="bbe65638-8786-4b30-a553-e6583df866a6">
      <Text>Green!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="205e3e77-c37b-4243-9347-0a76d9160c3e">
      <Text>ClAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="0bc952a4-17e5-43ad-9025-dd8742ce75e5">
      <Text>Yellow?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="General" id="3c4666c3-5b6f-4f95-a7fa-b2cf065ff328">
      <DualDialogue>
        <SpellCheckIgnoreLists>
          <IgnoredRanges/>
          <IgnoredWords/>
        </SpellCheckIgnoreLists>
        <Paragraph Type="Character" id="2aa98dfb-5a67-4e02-86ce-ba39014638e6">
          <Text>Ray (V.O.)</Text>
        </Paragraph>
        <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="729eaf10-e9e0-4478-93ef-6b27de66fb84">
          <Text Style="AllCaps">Green for crying out loud!</Text>
        </Paragraph>
        <Paragraph Type="Character" id="1ed3ffb0-1649-4fa1-a9c2-f2c015a7a7ec">
          <Text>KiDS (V.O.)</Text>
        </Paragraph>
        <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="01b66072-730f-46b9-9c20-f68a75b69fae">
          <Text Style="AllCaps">Green! Green! Green!</Text>
        </Paragraph>
      </DualDialogue>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="3aa1f8cc-f486-4b71-aed2-745cb8a413be">
      <Text>ClaY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="1e6b95de-ee4a-4b0c-8d24-ce88a79213e3">
      <Text>Ah! The </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">green</Text>
      <Text> planet! Do you have your sunglasses?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="afe3a7a8-311e-45ff-b057-0e54c1ebd3aa">
      <Text>Stardust puts on a pair of shades.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="b651c3a1-ce61-4db3-a473-41b010a4a756">
      <Text>Clay breaks into a catchy jingle.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="8348cd99-c1d8-4d14-b32b-8de53f05bcf9">
      <Text>ClaY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="136d6097-bf7b-4795-96a8-3676dbb1bfb8">
      <Text>Rocket, take us to the </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">green</Text>
      <Text>!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="ed93f298-3f0f-4f72-9c61-4111ad756278">
      <Text Style="AllCaps">Let’s land on this planet</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading" id="864571ec-4649-438f-8cb8-30e4ba8b6aa9">
      <SceneProperties Length="1 7/8" Page="2" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="CLAY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="CLAY &amp; RAY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="CLAY &amp; RAY &amp; KWAN">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="KWAN &amp; KIDS">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RAY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="STARDUST">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text Style="Bold+AllCaps">Int. Reyes Living Room - Day (2001)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="d3f18c5c-59a0-4800-a10e-8cb82beea391">
      <Text>A square TV plays the show. Ray</Text>
      <Text Size="10"> </Text>
      <Text>(4,</Text>
      <Text Size="10"> </Text>
      <Text>Filipina</Text>
      <Text Size="10"> </Text>
      <Text>American) dances along, in her homemade </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">cardboard rocket ship</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">costume</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="c7c940f6-d617-4188-9383-808824d35e4f">
      <Text>Clay &amp; Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="1cabf305-76c1-4ed4-9459-701592f22848">
      <Text Style="AllCaps">Let’s land on this planet
I wonder if we’ll call it home?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="d62c3c1b-1e34-4635-9255-1a4d23631325">
      <Text>Much like Clay, Ray turns to face her own “camera.”</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="e96a517a-6c7f-4030-b4f0-78eabd8e86d2">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="4468467e-fcf8-405d-bf11-3f46b1746db3">
      <Text>You my audience, welcome to mine home! I am Trini </Text>
      <Text Style="Italic">Reyes</Text>
      <Text>, friend of </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">Cway</Text>
      <Text>, wanna </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">pway</Text>
      <Text>?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="c7e7f514-878c-4a6e-af2c-2bdc4fe9c6a0">
      <Text>On the table, a </Text>
      <Text Style="Italic">Stardust</Text>
      <Text> coloring book lies open. Inside, a child’s messy coloring fills a page featuring Clay and the show’s creators: 
- </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">River Matthews</Text>
      <Text> (25, Ms. Frizzle-like) with Stardust puppet.
- </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">Schuyler “Skye” Park</Text>
      <Text> (26, Korean, in over their head).
- </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Style="AllCaps">Yaz</Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps"> “Ylem” </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Style="AllCaps">Lem</Text>
      <Text> (26, an animated animator).</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="d195e840-eb6d-425f-a91a-5a8eec70b1a0">
      <Text>Ray (O.S.)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="4468467e-fcf8-405d-bf11-3f46b1746db3">
      <Text>It so fun talkin’ to thin air!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="473dc14c-b5f2-42d1-a0e7-4ac47ea661c5">
      <Text Style="Bold+AllCaps">Montage - Five Years Later</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="e1d326e7-0cb3-4a21-8059-8af66c620b31">
      <Text Style="Bold">2002</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="969f8d5c-219f-40f9-830c-e2af0c7a9861">
      <Text>Rain hits the window. Ray (5) sits in the dark, out of her costume. She glances at the camera.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="48eaf312-bbf0-4a23-8101-4970eb226c48">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="6f3e4bcf-5500-4f67-8b1f-1d4627626d10">
      <Text>It can also be lonely...</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="969f8d5c-219f-40f9-830c-e2af0c7a9861">
      <Text>On the TV, Clay and Stardust drift in a black hole.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="46af8ae9-1b03-4fb1-8e5b-ea06088046d1">
      <Text>Stardust</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="bd2e39da-4499-44bf-ae34-411d5a0db280">
      <Text>Twinkle, twinkle, twinkle!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="e7942eea-d7fb-4829-b249-355e53a56913">
      <Text>Clay</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="ede10c2c-76d6-40c4-a8f6-3bfddd873595">
      <Text>Don't be scared! The darker it is, the more glitter we can see! You are not alone!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="7154dbc1-a968-4bed-a576-6f1be0f4d5dd">
      <Text>Reassured, Ray pulls her glittery rocket costume back on.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="11c4f04b-164d-4ac5-9fe9-3af43f2ecd97">
      <Text Style="Bold">2003</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="693045a6-1dee-4aac-987c-df18374906e5">
      <Text>Ray’s baby brother, </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">Kwan</Text>
      <Text>, crawls towards the TV screen. Ray (6) sits him down and crowns him an astronaut helmet.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="7e40c4d9-273d-43de-8aed-947da7315a9a">
      <Text>On the TV, Clay shows Stardust how to moonwalk. In the room, Ray helps Kwan take his first steps. He falls face first.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="f250beb9-7fdd-4eb5-ae7a-99d45da85804">
      <Text>ClAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="35dcdb54-86b3-4f1a-977a-020c0cf42510">
      <Text>Gravity’s the world giving us a</Text>
      <Text Size="10"> </Text>
      <Text>hug!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="bca6afec-b262-47ba-ba63-28a822cd768f">
      <Text Style="Bold">2004</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="c69df17c-25d1-4dfd-96fd-2c6061d1eceb">
      <Text>On the TV, Clay and Stardust sled across an icy comet. They pull out smoothies.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="ec74fc00-1741-4910-9646-127d7834a4fa">
      <Text>Clay</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="af464c30-ff8e-4c5f-9834-3e0b814dadaf">
      <Text>It’s not just a rock, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">stardusters</Text>
      <Text>. We’re sledding on a smoothie comet! Made of water, ice, </Text>
      <Text Style="Italic">dust</Text>
      <Text>, and sugar-</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="a534d806-ace4-41da-b6b7-0d7aaceda9ee">
      <Text>Ray (7) and Kwan (2) share a smoothie before wincing hard.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="General" id="88a172b8-f536-4e0a-8685-2044d04e3824">
      <DualDialogue>
        <SpellCheckIgnoreLists>
          <IgnoredRanges/>
          <IgnoredWords/>
        </SpellCheckIgnoreLists>
        <Paragraph Type="Character" id="1377fe92-b8a2-40e2-9fba-462e3177195a">
          <Text>Clay &amp; Ray &amp; Kwan</Text>
        </Paragraph>
        <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="052a6507-bb2b-42d7-bffc-6ad1097e3f46">
          <Text>Brain freeze!</Text>
        </Paragraph>
        <Paragraph Type="Character" id="491d5351-e082-4a7f-92fc-ecd3520e4aa1">
          <Text>Stardust</Text>
        </Paragraph>
        <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="ca90dfb4-5ca5-42cc-b94b-d6f929e537a0">
          <Text>Twinkle, twinkle, twinkle!</Text>
        </Paragraph>
      </DualDialogue>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="105744d0-1caf-4649-891e-6445cc5e6419">
      <Text Style="Bold">2005</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="ea93f9fd-823b-476d-a8c0-a1d8504d8fc4">
      <Text>Ray (8) performs a sock puppet show for Kwan (3) using Clay and Stardust socks. In the background, the real</Text>
      <Text Size="10"> </Text>
      <Text>TV</Text>
      <Text Size="10"> </Text>
      <Text>show</Text>
      <Text Size="10"> </Text>
      <Text>plays.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="ace7d802-c516-4728-8bf2-283673d81746">
      <Text>ClAY (o.S.)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="a2c5e6f5-80e7-44f0-bd2b-99eed0f554fc">
      <Text>What keeps our feet warm?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="a3671417-0ea8-4585-b997-05f80d7cac52">
      <Text>Kwan &amp; Kids (O.S.)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="edc760da-a434-42ce-b985-e98168e9550c">
      <Text>Socks!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="eafe5333-24af-47b9-b34b-762c1a9b6005">
      <Text>Clay (O.S.)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="3b5a1396-c024-463d-9220-9ad25cef1038">
      <Text>Gloves?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="acddfaad-a829-4055-8b8a-b9bca8d45b6f">
      <Text>Kwan &amp; Kids (O.S.)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="16e9f1ee-47e4-401a-b80b-f975208bfe5a">
      <Text>Socks! Socks! Socks!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="cd8b822d-f601-4e15-a073-decaf7ea56ef">
      <Text>ClAY (O.S.)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="efca0572-259c-46f6-93dd-fe32ba4f6b34">
      <Text>We’ve been on rocky planets, but have we ever visited a </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">socky</Text>
      <Text> one?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="88757235-aaee-4575-b201-71f20f9779fe">
      <Text>StarDUST (O.S.)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="54270937-3580-4631-be6c-49da85570a20">
      <Text>Twinkle, twinkle, twinkle!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="bcaa8ec8-db86-4fe9-b6c0-ed0fb336c967">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical" id="3a51bc9c-9b58-4fcc-ad37-29dda4472cdc">
      <Text>(Bowing)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="a3b554f8-cfd3-4c36-bc5f-18cbed70ddeb">
      <Text>Thanks for being my captive audience. You did me a solid, bruh.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading" id="f8e26f32-71ab-4cd7-b50d-e493d06a3ec6">
      <SceneProperties Length="1 3/8" Page="4" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="CLAY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="KIDS">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="KIDS &amp; KWAN">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="KWAN">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="PUPPET MASTER">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RAY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="STARDUST">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text Style="Bold+AllCaps">Int. Reyes Living Room - Day (2006)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="029619e5-77c7-4c12-933a-246589e1b67c">
      <Text>Ray (9) has passed her cardboard rocket down to Kwan (4). She sits on the sofa behind him, focused on her rehearsal booklet for </Text>
      <Text Style="Italic">A Christmas Carol</Text>
      <Text>, scribbling notes.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="08dd4788-a66d-441d-b997-9c90e6e2a594">
      <Text>On the TV, Clay (29) and Stardust sit on a tinfoil moon. Clay offers a bittersweet smile to the camera.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="9b6ecd6e-8695-4f00-82bf-6963ff445781">
      <Text>Clay</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="4452a36f-5db0-4f1c-9332-174f7f9c434e">
      <Text>When liquid becomes a gas, it doesn't go away. It just spreads out. It goes everywhere, like I am.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="c68e5431-9051-4285-8437-7e5009cbbe94">
      <Text>Stardust</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="eede606f-eb13-42d8-977d-349411e81858">
      <Text>Twinkle, twinkle, twinkle...</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="f7106e8c-d401-4c33-9476-ec6980dd7b21">
      <Text>ClAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="70713475-f2c1-4cb1-9502-46180b26eef8">
      <Text>‘specially behind the stars...</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="46ae151a-252d-46c8-abca-f9ece2c87e38">
      <Text>Kids (V.O.)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="3a46ccb1-e22c-477f-8209-d2f85583156b">
      <Text>Aww...</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="425df47e-56eb-4ae7-bcab-835a9086cc10">
      <Text>Ray looks up, annoyed that Kwan is blocking her view.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="90df1eb4-15f5-4926-9bbb-dbf13e2229cd">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="abc99818-0e7a-4cdd-bad6-2a825b061240">
      <Text>Bruh. You wanna go blind?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="7a3c00a5-1303-4d2d-95a6-d38e96f683ba">
      <Text>Kwan</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="2a7ee6c2-47b6-43d9-89ec-bba1fd509465">
      <Text>Like you’ll be, Tiny Trini?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="db27cda8-18ec-46b6-830f-455720672db4">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="6bb0cd99-2e48-426b-940e-6a903a61d20c">
      <Text Style="Italic">Tiny Tim</Text>
      <Text> ain’t blind... Kwan, sit further away from the TV.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="01212214-c653-422d-86de-ada48b2b8e2b">
      <Text>ClAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="f330da80-a1c8-484c-ac8f-d7680913432e">
      <Text>I must go home now. Time to say?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="d607c104-be1f-47d4-a5b5-f06832f64bc7">
      <Text>Kids &amp; Kwan</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="bfd5b90e-7288-4335-beef-5d6296cfe274">
      <Text>Goodbye...</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="0cc02f09-57e1-4c9f-badf-ff99a55192ef">
      <Text>CLAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="d4b58cf0-7936-46db-a41a-098c66f2cc31">
      <Text>But you? You’re already home. Trust in yourself, Stardust.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="be2969ca-3261-401a-afb9-63d719d2787e">
      <Text>Clay boards Rocket. The ship blasts off into the cosmos. Stardust pulses with a final spark and vanishes.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="8d23f68b-c7d7-4dcf-9bb8-61142c2059a5">
      <Text>The screen fades to black. The text appears: “Clay Goes Home.” A final production still of the team and studio follows: “Thank you for 7 years of </Text>
      <Text Style="Italic">Stardust</Text>
      <Text>.”</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="9c92b40e-fdde-4527-98ab-2f80d5ff57bd">
      <Text>Ray drops her pen, finally giving the TV</Text>
      <Text Size="10"> </Text>
      <Text>her</Text>
      <Text Size="10"> </Text>
      <Text>full</Text>
      <Text Size="10"> </Text>
      <Text>attention.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="c7a5d551-16e2-49aa-95d9-5178a53e654e">
      <Text>RAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="84c32215-8252-4b01-aad1-1b7e505884f9">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">Wuh</Text>
      <Text>-No “See ya later, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">stardusters</Text>
      <Text>?”</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="ab0e784a-e211-4428-866f-aeb5417346ac">
      <Text>Ray joins Kwan at the TV. A reflection of two small kids stare back in the glass. She looks down at her pen.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="General" id="8040202a-a476-4a83-a2be-88ac2b841c85">
      <DualDialogue>
        <SpellCheckIgnoreLists>
          <IgnoredRanges/>
          <IgnoredWords/>
        </SpellCheckIgnoreLists>
        <Paragraph Type="Character" id="b325a6d1-31cf-4249-ad07-741ebbf3a253">
          <Text>Kwan</Text>
        </Paragraph>
        <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="7f75a458-cf9d-4aec-ba25-500ecf225665">
          <Text>Goodbye Clay...</Text>
        </Paragraph>
        <Paragraph Type="Character" id="55a9980a-5f0b-4170-829f-e7ff88d1830f">
          <Text>RAY</Text>
        </Paragraph>
        <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="4e4f110f-4dde-41fb-b5e6-798a9e036528">
          <Text>Hello Ray...</Text>
        </Paragraph>
      </DualDialogue>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="39a9027c-28de-4bd6-8a62-7480d117dd9d">
      <Text>With sudden purpose, she opens the checkout card inside her booklet and crosses out “Trini Reyes.” In its place, she writes </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">Ray</Text>
      <Text> in bold letters. She holds it up to the camera.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Transition" id="952f419d-0561-4a75-b97b-b0e347eda6f8">
      <Text>Match cut to:</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading" id="bd85ea9d-ac45-4f84-afd8-5620fbfb4c39">
      <SceneProperties Length="1 3/8" Page="5" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="GIRL">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="KIDS">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RAY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text Style="Bold+AllCaps">Int. Detroit House - Day (2025)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="713c5756-8762-4179-82d0-19104ba00a06">
      <Text>A flyer features an illustration of Ray (29) and a bold graphic: "</Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">Ray, the star for your birthday!</Text>
      <Text>"</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="76014097-2598-46d8-9445-7ba65a7ce11c">
      <Text>The flyer lowers to reveal Ray at a space-themed party. The decor is depressing, even the wallpaper is bored. Ray stands behind a table draped in a shiny tarp littered with plastic spaceships. She wears a lab coat that has seen better days.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="202a3664-bd40-4a4c-9e91-41c38cc3568c">
      <Text>Behind her, a mountain of gift boxes looms like a threat.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="2c827bef-1120-4486-a0a2-6278a4ea8c7b">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="d177e896-b4e2-4cc7-a523-46d146e6fb15">
      <Text>Welcome future doctors, lawyers, and engineers! Those who want to break glass ceilings!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical" id="88a403a3-87ef-4ccb-9a56-e570959bedcd">
      <Text>(to camera)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="f673a349-b457-4e63-ba46-3f7f7e729b26">
      <Text>Because no one wants to break fourth walls like actors...</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical" id="2a656e5d-d75e-4f8a-94bf-13949d8efff7">
      <Text>(to the kids)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="d177e896-b4e2-4cc7-a523-46d146e6fb15">
      <Text>You’ve heard of a lightning in a bottle. Wanna trap a supernova?!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="7b8d288f-7bc5-47f5-b287-2800aa532db8">
      <Text>The children stare, unimpressed. A </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">birthday girl</Text>
      <Text> (8) ignores it all and punches data into a spreadsheet on her tablet.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="d73759d7-2665-454c-b03c-a7a2cc0847c8">
      <Text>Girl</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="ffd0c439-91e5-42e8-afe1-e703b236ae83">
      <Text>Mom says science is a hobby for losers who can’t do math.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="2c885db7-1525-4df1-90a2-cfbb13b54e75">
      <Text>Ray’s eye twitches. She forces a smile, reaching for a glass beaker filled with a swirling liquid.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="5799c428-f2b1-4ac8-ace6-89903cca2f20">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="6d94bdc5-6463-4e99-9b31-a7e407e6b88d">
      <Text>Well, birthday gal, clearly your mom can’t do math cause no iPad kid should be younger than seven and you’re?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="6186071a-4f3b-474a-9657-c51c094150b3">
      <Text>KidS</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="1e9b1ca6-1edc-42c5-ab1b-babe30f774ec">
      <Text>Six!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="aa629902-9ea3-4116-83fb-495649abc281">
      <Text>Ray takes away the girl’s tablet and sets it on the table.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="6bb0a3bc-9740-4370-8948-9f7c439c016c">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="686d0a05-4734-472b-9e0a-2e97d6b06f8a">
      <Text>But you can never be too young for chemicals! Will you do the honors?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="b75bc80d-73ad-474e-b538-720613a70670">
      <Text>Ray hands the girl a small vial.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="7d39d944-fdf4-4e61-8d6b-20c2da33fc30">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical" id="f9b2fde3-45a9-4a59-91b0-c1e5a594393d">
      <Text>(to camera)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="90287ed0-7581-45ec-89f6-c2f72037cbaf">
      <Text>Is this where the magic begins? Or is this where the lawsuit begins? Magic or lawsuit...? Suit yourself.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="8ff752e4-0453-45c0-ad3f-d29599ffaf94">
      <Text>The girl drops the vial in. The liquid becomes colorful.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="a2489c59-f757-4f78-be6a-f6015a43a74c">
      <Text>RAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="8d01592f-d666-4a48-a8b4-e8d9d9a86ecb">
      <Text>Behold! A supernova-</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="f81790c2-7fa5-4870-b30f-e1841cdd8125">
      <Text>Girl</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="953aa769-7c97-43f7-a2bf-91e1610f359e">
      <Text>Is it supposed to smell like you?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="2cce51d6-57ee-4483-adfc-d8bd32ebbb90">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical" id="23ee4220-b2af-4136-aa63-e0b153f241a3">
      <Text>(Offended)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="b32b9a35-c794-4920-a058-d5fb0cb1245a">
      <Text Style="Italic">Excuse</Text>
      <Text>...</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="4d7d62b2-3e88-4076-9b24-2a9fbb231216">
      <Text>The beaker hisses and vibrates. Ray’s eyes widens. She lunges and shields the girl with her coat.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="afa709c8-ce7e-4a67-bcc2-e01fa380c39c">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="c32642fd-5dda-4d29-90dd-8c555468d413">
      <Text>...</Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">me</Text>
      <Text>!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading" id="8f12d86b-d97d-463a-9a7e-eb4206128b0e">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="7" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RAY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text Style="Bold+AllCaps">Ext. Detroit House - ContinUOUS</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="fe4a06f2-6639-4e68-9508-0e15cedadbbf">
      <Text Style="AllCaps">Boom</Text>
      <Text>. A rainbow-colored fog erupts from the windows, swallowing the house. The kids scream to the high heavens. The door swings open. Ray dizzily pops out.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="9bc83af3-17d6-46a7-9d33-b66fea21591e">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical" id="86c53af7-40d5-4647-8216-c9e0750ede91">
      <Text>(to camera)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="06f13ff2-9082-4420-a41e-3e7433549663">
      <Text>That’s the smell of discovery! Side effects include sounds of terror...</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Center" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.00" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="End of Act" id="8320508a-6b7a-43cd-9457-386c90d1a8a4">
      <Text>End of Cold Open</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="e7d4a034-ce3c-4897-b63b-991f7dd19c3b">
      <Text Style="Bold+AllCaps">Begin Main Titles</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="1a28fe51-38f0-4a48-b283-3a03a5ed2811">
      <Text>“Just a Phase” sung by River Matthews plays.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="1a28fe51-38f0-4a48-b283-3a03a5ed2811">
      <Text Style="AllCaps">Montage</Text>
      <Text>:</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="8c2fa7ef-19b1-48ca-bbea-4f48bbedd059">
      <Text>- Ray (29) and Kwan (24) board a cardboard rocket ship and blast off into a cardboard cosmos.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="4a691660-4582-43c0-a202-1611a3cefd9e">
      <Text>- </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">Ms. Aurora Starling</Text>
      <Text> (29, Biracial, perfect) glides past them, looking flawless in a pristine cardboard spacesuit.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="603f2c17-7b69-40cd-bddc-a097db4cd1f5">
      <Text>- Ray and Kwan’s rocket crash lands on a strange world.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="006659d1-bbed-480c-a51e-319403d1528a">
      <Text>- On this new world, Clay appears, dancing with Stardust and her pink axolotl sister, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Style="AllCaps">StarPower</Text>
      <Text>. River pops out from behind Stardust and </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">StarPower</Text>
      <Text>, while Skye and puppeteer Ylem join them, surrounded by many other cosmic characters. They wave directly to the audience.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="62db2a78-ea2f-4c09-a492-4854f26afbcf">
      <Text>- The camera zooms out to reveal the previous scene is playing on a square TV. Ray and Kwan are perched on top of this TV, posing with their own Stardust-inspired puppets.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="fdd6baaa-4aa0-414e-bd83-064ebb2aa9e6">
      <Text>- The </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">Solid, Liquid, and Gas</Text>
      <Text> title graphic appears on the TV respectively above Clay, River, and Skye. Then expands out.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="4e78583b-4417-485e-a677-f3ffb92564ac">
      <Text Style="Bold+AllCaps">End Main Titles</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="New Act" id="c74f8479-2577-41ab-979b-f9185f8cb475">
      <Text>Act One</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading" id="71bd4133-3b90-462f-8b6c-22f5f623db18">
      <SceneProperties Length="7/8" Page="8" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="HOPE">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RAY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text Style="Bold+AllCaps">Ext. Detroit House - Day</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="39d2ff3f-a0af-4088-ad2c-22724c964cdc">
      <Text>All windows and doors are open to vent out the chaos earlier. A disheveled Ray sits on the curb. Her lab coat is singed.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="5142ecd2-4042-4d3e-b6b4-15b36367df25">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical" id="27817e43-7b20-40ac-99f4-084e34423292">
      <Text>(to camera)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="2742e5be-62b4-4e41-afb2-87058ff027ac">
      <Text>Do you see hope... around here? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="39d2ff3f-a0af-4088-ad2c-22724c964cdc">
      <Text Style="AllCaps">Hope</Text>
      <Text> (40s), the homeowner, emerges with the charred tablet.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="e29e0bfc-b3a6-4a56-ad72-760e3d909f11">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="5ed0b874-7084-4816-acce-bcd2a5a8ad3a">
      <Text>Hope! Your look is on fleek-</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="f399c875-b417-466f-afd3-63c80af43a9f">
      <Text>Hope</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="fba8a723-4e94-4eb7-a998-738de54e314a">
      <Text>Stop this flamboyance. I thought your days of setting things on fire were over.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="9cfc1db8-bed0-4119-824e-c7e95cdecbe5">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="d9fbceea-c8b7-4712-bbcd-e0b976b5da12">
      <Text Style="Italic">Flamboyance</Text>
      <Text> is derived from the verb, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Style="Italic">flamboyer</Text>
      <Text>, meaning to flame-</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="eb505f74-09f9-45b3-9bd0-e2e9b2e7bb7f">
      <Text>Hope</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="6b8be0b7-c59e-46cf-8cd3-9746246f3079">
      <Text>You’re fired! For real this time. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="df141a67-8fee-467d-8d08-d38897ce351a">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="ebfbe2f2-f6a9-486e-a5be-94f1bd64bedb">
      <Text>Hope! Ugh, your name makes no sense-</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="f27e92eb-9750-498e-a54c-9ed99f8c06ae">
      <Text>HopE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="e684a198-074c-4f82-ab16-325c314645b8">
      <Text>My niece’s birthday was your chance to cool off after burning all our puppets before the national tour even started-</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="95cd08a5-0d14-4a8d-b812-165170f83072">
      <Text>RAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="ce2f2505-79bd-4e6f-92de-4690d24eeca7">
      <Text>It was an accident...</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="15c704c2-6449-46f1-8535-919afcd39e84">
      <Text>HopE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="6a81711e-28ef-47da-84a7-d3f90f2fc545">
      <Text>I can only hope you accidentally find a new purpose in life.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="e7d92139-1208-4004-9855-ebd19cb5f9ce">
      <Text>Hope walks away, leaving Ray to despair alone.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading" id="d0e659f8-8220-454a-8e8e-858b26c1ac52">
      <SceneProperties Length="3/8" Page="8" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RAY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text Style="Bold+AllCaps">Int. Ray’s Car - Day</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="0ff5acd1-7a2a-45d9-85aa-b7e373417f65">
      <Text>Ray sees herself in the rearview mirror. She</Text>
      <Text Size="10"> </Text>
      <Text>faces</Text>
      <Text Size="10"> </Text>
      <Text>the</Text>
      <Text Size="10"> </Text>
      <Text>camera.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="c041c0b4-4a7f-4f50-b9c2-a35f5f560453">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="6792307a-c42a-4347-bddf-26ea1a9c40e6">
      <Text>What now, world? Should I go look for another job or should I... ...ill myself.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="6eb2e6dc-12bd-4007-8f4e-a0a138e2e76e">
      <Text>Ray motions like she is slitting her own throat.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="9edb49d9-c82d-499e-bb4b-3176cf07e1ca">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="102d5404-4d9e-4659-9a5c-772ddf2365e8">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">Whichhhhh</Text>
      <Text> one...? Apply myself or </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">offffffff</Text>
      <Text> myself?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="ae1218f8-9031-42fa-9d7b-d9e96b891fdc">
      <Text>Ray watches the birthday girl walk by with Hope. The girl waves approvingly while Hope makes a slitting throat motion.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading" id="4d363499-15c2-4609-832f-b7fe0e32ac7f">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="9" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RAY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text Style="Bold+AllCaps">Ext. Ray’s Car - Continuous</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="f1b9fb0e-6dbb-4515-bfc7-e5581fe4b86b">
      <Text>Ray drives away.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="98a468ff-eb9c-4f54-aeaa-1d32f40292e4">
      <Text>Ray (V.O.)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="f6f9fadd-f734-461b-bc37-cf86bd32174b">
      <Text>Alright, world. Perhaps, I should ask: What’s next?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading" id="57d90b96-27b1-47a6-9269-6c3170445e33">
      <SceneProperties Length="1 5/8" Page="9" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="CLAY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text Style="Bold+AllCaps">Int. Ray’s Car - Day</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="dbce47fb-2e46-4d45-bd18-55d2ab3ffac0">
      <Text>Ray’s phone, mounted on the dash, </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">pings</Text>
      <Text>. A notification banner slides across: </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">Ms. Aurora is Live!</Text>
      <Text> (42K Watching).</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="acb24d4c-72ed-4d43-80aa-23abc0cc0ad9">
      <Text>Ray </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">swipes</Text>
      <Text> away the notification. Her thumb accidentally hits a different video: </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">Billy Clayton Dubois</Text>
      <Text> (45), the original Clay, sits in a sunny garden wearing his iconic cosmic vest.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="80574043-de3c-47dc-9dcb-86c47117ee12">
      <Text>Clay</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="8eded6ab-e3f0-4e7a-8d4a-dd54f2cd7042">
      <Text>Hey. You got a moment?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="565e605d-b13b-488b-8e0d-a778d94e7273">
      <Text>Ray reaches out to swipe him away, but her hand trembles and drops. She lets him speak. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="dad41a06-cadb-4439-8742-3c86da72c5d1">
      <Text>ClAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="8eded6ab-e3f0-4e7a-8d4a-dd54f2cd7042">
      <Text>Alright. You remember how when we were younger, we used to run around and hang out with Stardust and discover her stuff and ride Rocket and get lost on another planet and solve all the fun </Text>
      <Text Style="Italic">clues</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="eed34732-79ac-4272-9585-323456b3de8d">
      <Text>Ray sniffles, her eyes darting between the road and screen. On screen, Clay leans in with a smile as warm as a blanket.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="59aa9c23-5a82-4172-bdc7-53ec285edb20">
      <Text>CLAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="8eded6ab-e3f0-4e7a-8d4a-dd54f2cd7042">
      <Text>But one day I said, “Guess what? Huge news: I’m returning to my home planet.” And then Rocket took me away and we were gone. And we didn’t see each other for like an eternity. Want to talk about that?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="fce42656-61b9-4ac3-b41c-e15f62305046">
      <Text>Ray reluctantly nods. She feels like a five-year-old again.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="9e479f43-8b8a-4ade-a2da-bdb7bfd25906">
      <Text>Clay</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="78f908aa-9c47-40a8-bf3f-4c6b3d710373">
      <Text>I realize it was sorta spontaneous. I just took Rocket for a spin and went on a much needed vacation. And that was super challenging by the way. But great cause I got to rest my head and take things slowly and now I’m literally doing all sorts of things that I dreamt of doing.

And then look at you and all you’ve done and all you’ve accomplished in all that time and it’s just... it’s just awesome, am I right? I mean we started out with stuff and now it’s what? Rent, and jobs, and families.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="a8b13682-f36b-4bf8-a71a-fe2fa818bb40">
      <Text>Ray aggressively flips a FAMILY PHOTO face down on the passenger seat, hiding the happy faces of her and her family.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="d354ae10-2a5d-4146-ba35-a64068da7d6e">
      <Text>Clay</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="e2dfb5b9-9c8a-4a89-8266-c0ceb75b570e">
      <Text>And some of it has been </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">kinda</Text>
      <Text> hard, you know? I know you know. And I hoped to tell you that I really couldn’t have done all of that without your help. And in fact, all the singing you did when I was singing back when we were younger still rings music to my ears today. Right now. And that’s truly dope.
</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="cec3cddb-7cfd-42ae-90eb-5094b5e61517">
      <Text>I guess I wanted to say: After an eternity, I never forgot you, ever. And I’m super glad we’re forever buddies. Thanks for listening.

You look fabulous by the way. Whatever you’re doing, it’s working.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="2a71ac33-c972-4a34-b958-cffe49f80274">
      <Text>Ray catches her reflection in the rearview mirror of a disheveled, unemployed mess.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="89e31cb5-4416-4e87-841c-42782f343c3e">
      <Text>The video ends, replaced by a </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">Stardust 25th Anniversary</Text>
      <Text> graphic. Ray swipes it away, pulling up a map. The destination: </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">East Lansing, Michigan</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading" id="b6e35718-0e1e-4b9c-af91-ee9b1a813231">
      <SceneProperties Length="1/8" Page="10" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats/>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text Style="Bold+AllCaps">Ext. Michigan State University - Afternoon</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="2e20ed32-4742-4334-a176-2dbeedead880">
      <Text>Ray’s car rolls onto the sprawling campus.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading" id="f08d061a-559f-41df-9b0e-4f1bc2b369a4">
      <SceneProperties Length="3/8" Page="10" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RAY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text Style="Bold+AllCaps">Int. Ray’s Car - ConTINUOUS</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="2fbdba88-6f3c-4c9f-bda5-f5eea1db8071">
      <Text>Ray hits “record live” on her phone and forces a smile.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="dd992267-07ef-43f4-8fdd-94b8ba5327e0">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="89efe9b4-0012-4ac9-8c58-80e91efd948e">
      <Text>Plasma update: I’m in East Lansing to get our hands dirty in astronomy-</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="57b2c369-692a-43e7-a3a2-506b2b572b76">
      <Text>A notification pops up on the screen. A comment from @ClimateChangeIsFake: “earth is flat, plasma girl.”</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="89a4f172-8540-4d93-a63e-8c5853038268">
      <Text>Ray winces at the camera. Her thumb clicks the </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">block</Text>
      <Text> button.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="674ccb46-fb46-4ec1-ba9b-e2a3d794c5ff">
      <Text>RaY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="89efe9b4-0012-4ac9-8c58-80e91efd948e">
      <Text Style="Italic">Blocking conspiracy theorists</Text>
      <Text>. Actually, we’re here to see if my genius brother can explain why our universe is a dumpster fire.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading" id="d6e6682e-8d3d-4547-8695-9c277971e902">
      <SceneProperties Length="6/8" Page="11" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="KWAN">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RAY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text Style="Bold+AllCaps">Ext. Abrams Planetarium Parking Lot - CoNTINUOUS</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="4fc7e1d6-4004-4d67-9528-5a9c4b3e4803">
      <Text>Ray pulls into a spot and stops recording.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="4fc7e1d6-4004-4d67-9528-5a9c4b3e4803">
      <Text>Ray stares at Kwan, standing with other </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">college students</Text>
      <Text> by the planetarium. She points to them.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="4ddf48f9-5aea-40bd-929e-a9b8479657e8">
      <Text>RAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical" id="d68aacd5-d81f-464f-862d-924d624ddea5">
      <Text>(to camera)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="ed8956ef-7773-47b1-9b01-7d6061bc80a8">
      <Text>Can you find my brother?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical" id="43e3ed99-cc04-4fde-9596-8b48216498a3">
      <Text>(pointing at Kwan)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="acad7f28-fa9f-4619-95eb-5be267e80935">
      <Text>This is my brother? What makes you think this goofball is my brother?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="9623537b-16c8-4b6c-9c9f-8c55cea05026">
      <Text>Kwan notices Ray’s car and approaches.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="a8988995-0b6c-40d5-9e73-3a7c61118dbe">
      <Text Style="AllCaps">Thump. Thump. Thump.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="67bba11d-1aad-4401-b86f-6641b1040db4">
      <Text>Ray jumps, gasping. Kwan, wearing an </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">MSU</Text>
      <Text> hoodie and noise-canceling headphones around his neck, taps the car window.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="c42a2c69-7100-43d1-b54c-549f252e977a">
      <Text>Kwan</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="b479e77f-d063-4bd4-9e38-bd9294cb2f80">
      <Text>It’s just Sunshine. You looked like you’ve touched the sun...?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="26267c3d-2bd5-4309-8180-da9d83798dda">
      <Text>RAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="40021939-f6e6-4088-b6d9-8575d3fe86d1">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">Pfffff</Text>
      <Text> nah, bruh. And that nickname is never catching on!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="a8de143f-2c87-4434-a45b-949eb344f2e7">
      <Text>KWAN</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="bbba2242-e2e1-4952-935c-ac923134c219">
      <Text>If not that, the planetarium has some new animations that might interested you!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="3d55b5b1-1a05-4d85-8a64-91c8c40c20b2">
      <Text>Ray gets out of the car and follows Kwan to the planetarium.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading" id="a9b55b7d-a5b0-4836-97f1-c785f3b09dc0">
      <SceneProperties Length="1 3/8" Page="12" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="KWAN">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RAY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text Style="Bold+AllCaps">Int. Abrams Planetarium - Day</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="0011ce00-5720-4f12-8caf-7240984a8254">
      <Text>Ray and Kwan pass a meteorite exhibit as he leads her into the dimly lit dome. Kwan heads to the control console. He taps the keys, causing the dome sky to ripple in stars.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="f640b0a0-24f4-499e-abb7-a70600a2a05b">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="9b32350b-43cc-47e3-b1bf-a28406d7663f">
      <Text>Wow... Time to get lit.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="05dd18fc-40dc-447c-8fb0-6b8683d0d339">
      <Text>KWAN</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="df335041-d180-4499-b178-2a526871a858">
      <Text>This universe you see, it’s real.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="be24fa83-f9be-45ab-9c7b-37f35128d36c">
      <Text>RAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="b235f5c3-740f-4412-b483-3bb7151d788d">
      <Text>I wish I could live here, bruh. No producers, puppets, just darkness.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="62c373e0-c38c-402d-a32b-c3309b43e5a0">
      <Text>The dome displays auroras.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="7c97731f-5a6a-4787-9ea6-0d608e363742">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="6972a1a6-84f7-4552-bf8e-e1a34c49a960">
      <Text>Please no auroras...</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="4ecd8cfe-38dc-42c9-82e5-3da5bad36da2">
      <Text>Ray pulls out a group photo, displaying it to the camera. She points to Aurora Starling (17, perfect) next to Ray (17).</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="e0bf96ed-034a-4406-ae72-54bbcd41f3d5">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="49a54e86-a7d7-4f12-829e-b8140ccc7ba6">
      <Text>That perfect Ms. Aurora Starling. We ain’t seen eye to eye since theatre camp, Girls State, college.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="59ce4f9d-2a26-40d9-8438-66a3b9098753">
      <Text>KwaN</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="85f0be4b-f995-4c1f-9b39-772806eb9a5b">
      <Text>Auroras are the best, especially Ms. Aurora. Her YouTube channel makes me wanna touch grass. Your channel makes me feel kidnapped-</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="5ebd99f5-a4a5-4445-9b90-a5f05fcb061f">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical" id="49da5dca-975c-4fe6-99f6-4b97b25e8d87">
      <Text>(in Tagalog; subtitled)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="ffbd5864-5028-4ae2-a065-bfbf4e7765ac">
      <Text>Shut up.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="7830515c-6a8b-48ee-85a4-3a7e6c7c50ac">
      <Text>A </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">supernova</Text>
      <Text> blooms across the dome.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="8a681b79-91f6-4ffa-829a-72b1fe68c89c">
      <Text>Kwan</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="9e829236-b483-49c4-a421-482d31c56fb8">
      <Text>How about a supernova for size? “Twinkle, twinkle, twinkle.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="a5a85fd2-0660-482a-9cf9-089cfc3d795a">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="3eaa38a6-ddf1-4a87-80bd-4a716470e60e">
      <Text>Such a blast from the past. I miss </Text>
      <Text Style="Italic">Stardust</Text>
      <Text>. What a great show.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="108a13ad-77cb-43cf-8184-44ccfa21add9">
      <Text>Kwan</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="1613115d-be9f-4760-ba86-276056371bf4">
      <Text>Stardust is here.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="82a1c634-56f9-48a3-89d6-cc1536aab1c6">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="fded4964-a66d-4c5b-83c4-ce012230bde5">
      <Text>And so is Clay in our hearts...</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="2bc80a6c-a7d3-4411-9485-88bdbc68e1f1">
      <Text>Kwan</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="4b7f565e-1eb0-432d-8518-c93ea457218d">
      <Text>No, Stardust is visiting tomorrow.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="cedc4a52-33e0-4db5-8211-58464d7866fe">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="042c71ff-d70c-48cc-ba21-1b9cd4410bbf">
      <Text>What? In what world is she-</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="48544668-87f1-47aa-bc52-75b377d1323a">
      <Text>Kwan pulls out an </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Style="AllCaps">MSU</Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps"> Arts Fair</Text>
      <Text> flyer. The graphic features River Matthews (50) holding her Stardust puppet and </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">text</Text>
      <Text>: “Master of Ceremony: River Matthews, </Text>
      <Text Style="Italic">Stardust </Text>
      <Text>Creator.”</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="cac81c94-8759-4e9e-aa8f-33cd38619354">
      <Text>Ray celebrates and dances about.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="5c15f6f0-0aa8-4d88-8b97-8ee257624f1c">
      <Text>KwaN</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="d570f910-5975-48c7-bb0d-d119ea97aed4">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">Shhhhhhhhh</Text>
      <Text>!!!!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="e55801bf-1871-4bd6-99cb-282513b5fd75">
      <Text>Ray collects herself and smiles at the camera.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading" id="ef801fc1-2729-412e-91e2-b16efc470bc0">
      <SceneProperties Length="2" Page="13" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="CLAY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="KIDS">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="KWAN">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RAY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="ROCKET">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="STARDUST">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text Style="Bold+AllCaps">Int. Kwan’s Apartment - Night</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="03270387-028a-490a-b435-4a3bbb751a2b">
      <Text>Physics posters fill the walls, telescopes scatter around the spaces, and unresolved assignments lie stacked on a table.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="03270387-028a-490a-b435-4a3bbb751a2b">
      <Text>Ray lies on the floor, surrounded by takeout containers. Kwan peeks out of the bathroom, brushing his teeth.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="dc037c4d-98cd-4370-9ef4-f9657bd6cb5b">
      <Text>RAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="a4ecdb54-ab1c-46a5-bf0c-5fe48c4bdc0e">
      <Text>I’m a black hole of food, bruh.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="9905ad20-7f41-458e-a5ae-73f2c221a6a5">
      <Text>Kwan spits out the toothpaste and rinses his toothbrush.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="3efaeff9-c2de-4c08-8dec-358ffe72696e">
      <Text>KWAN</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="2b6270a4-54c2-4f25-b5b0-bded1588973e">
      <Text>You’re really a supernova.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="2065cabc-21b5-4646-b82a-f227412b82a7">
      <Text>RAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="7d677471-4b70-4b49-9ece-9c7fe4f12c2a">
      <Text>Thanks, bruh. That’s actually—</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="7999c914-d3a9-4d22-8733-6beb8a80db8b">
      <Text>KWAN</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="dbf668ed-6b7a-47a8-9e03-9633c2970104">
      <Text>Supernova is a messy violent implosion caused by the inability to manage pressure... and food.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="a1c96c49-2d12-4ba6-8fcc-c6f3e71dfc32">
      <Text>RaY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical" id="04e5735b-c711-4cf1-b132-82da5c95cf20">
      <Text>(in Tagalog; subtitled)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="c4c87567-e6aa-4c32-8fca-acad82e7870c">
      <Text>Shut the hell up!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="24c1e334-de72-4886-bbc7-600c9a3ea98e">
      <Text>Kwan heads off to bed.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="3d159850-7270-43bb-b049-b169f97351fe">
      <Text>RAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="3993a229-0807-4109-a14b-d72aba15b333">
      <Text>I was trying to save my puppet show-</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="be023109-0950-4a7c-86c9-42dab68f0397">
      <Text>Kwan (O.S.)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="c67ff3b0-6261-42cf-b192-0d0a30faec58">
      <Text>Maybe it’s a time you stop saving and start listening.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="f2eb96ae-3dd6-4c59-ac23-aee0eedf5f61">
      <Text>Ray sits upright against the sofa. She grabs the remote and turns on the flatscreen TV. From the </Text>
      <Text Style="Italic">Stardust</Text>
      <Text> catalog on a streaming app, she selects a classic episode: “ZINC!”</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="b651c3a1-ce61-4db3-a473-41b010a4a756">
      <Text Style="Bold">ON THE TV:</Text>
      <Text> A rocket ship touches down on a vibrant, hand-painted planet. Rocket sings a jingle.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="1fba0e28-ce16-413d-9d5a-c5f89f1dd76c">
      <Text>Rocket</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="538e12d0-902a-4e31-87ed-5307d57e3832">
      <Text Style="AllCaps">Let’s land on this planet
I wonder if we’ll call it home?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="b651c3a1-ce61-4db3-a473-41b010a4a756">
      <Text>Clay (20s) steps out of the hatch into a whimsical forest. He comes across a strange, glowing purple mushroom.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="44a5c628-a1fb-4ebd-846b-b18ccdb07779">
      <Text>CLAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="84f19451-bd27-44ff-add3-e52223b84af2">
      <Text>What color is that?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="8b9ea3d2-fac4-42d6-89b8-453091f4a2cd">
      <Text>Kids (V.O.)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="e4f35b36-9f0f-4749-93e5-e2f25c609680">
      <Text>Purple!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="29d96b29-32b7-4ebb-9c2f-7082bfbd2bff">
      <Text>ClAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="634f35bc-0972-46c1-b994-52e22912a18c">
      <Text>Green?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="a60bf764-cbf8-48a2-a458-bae372f147db">
      <Text>Ray turns to the camera with an amused look.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="General" id="6bc6b778-f22d-4337-ab07-e8ee6c13b46f">
      <DualDialogue>
        <SpellCheckIgnoreLists>
          <IgnoredRanges/>
          <IgnoredWords/>
        </SpellCheckIgnoreLists>
        <Paragraph Type="Character" id="5188fa66-623e-4e23-b31e-70e256226934">
          <Text>RAY</Text>
        </Paragraph>
        <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="9975702f-de3e-44f3-8147-c6488fb88567">
          <Text>This guy’s so colorblind...</Text>
        </Paragraph>
        <Paragraph Type="Character" id="ad7f43ce-2890-438b-bb0b-33dbd00fd37f">
          <Text>Kids (V.O.)</Text>
        </Paragraph>
        <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="9efa9bd8-2938-4e12-a46a-5f7b39eca55e">
          <Text Style="AllCaps">Purple! Purple! Purple!</Text>
        </Paragraph>
      </DualDialogue>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="0b1d9e64-d22e-46f3-9ff9-d022bb3e89f1">
      <Text>CLAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="e00dd134-e89e-4157-adf1-d24242017c1a">
      <Text>A </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">purple</Text>
      <Text> mushroom! Stardust, should we check it out?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="33a29262-621f-4b4b-bab0-f392e3a140c7">
      <Text>Stardust zips around Clay’s head, leaving a trail of glitter before landing on the sprout with a musical </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">ding</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="23e80774-b7d0-4e22-9524-3dfe3d3cae57">
      <Text>Stardust</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="99f584f0-adfe-4da3-bb17-74fe1f48540c">
      <Text>Twinkle, twinkle, twinkle!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="f20f75c6-4d8c-4d76-8f57-c54c145d6cd1">
      <Text>Clay</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="a757dc5d-c1f3-4e2b-8239-8b2d776d23bf">
      <Text>You’re right, Stardust. It does feel cold... </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">Brrr</Text>
      <Text>! How cold?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="1b26cc81-c1d8-45e8-86e5-8e76a185f564">
      <Text>Rocket</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="8eb2e49f-e334-4839-be7b-5912cc48efcc">
      <Text>Temperature is thirty below zero! Even fungus here are ice cold!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="ed267782-d961-44fd-a5b6-97f93843bc7a">
      <Text>CLAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="c5ee2428-8082-449c-a061-9d855969f287">
      <Text>Ice is a...?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="General" id="603c5f85-215b-49f7-a9ee-ed7ac6754c6b">
      <DualDialogue>
        <SpellCheckIgnoreLists>
          <IgnoredRanges/>
          <IgnoredWords/>
        </SpellCheckIgnoreLists>
        <Paragraph Type="Character" id="1a50e6e4-de38-4fa5-8660-e5c0b05702a9">
          <Text>RAY</Text>
        </Paragraph>
        <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="eec6820f-0ae2-4429-96b9-88eb122ed04b">
          <Text>Evil.</Text>
        </Paragraph>
        <Paragraph Type="Character" id="52bea605-497c-4172-9434-81c82411f5fe">
          <Text>KidS</Text>
        </Paragraph>
        <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="b32664a5-72d7-4e61-a429-e9bdab7a1df5">
          <Text>Solid!</Text>
        </Paragraph>
      </DualDialogue>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="394ea903-f5b7-49e9-a39b-84210ae865cf">
      <Text>Clay</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="c5ee2428-8082-449c-a061-9d855969f287">
      <Text>Solid! It stays one shape. But when-</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="ac10f861-5e25-48ef-be38-4f260fbfae60">
      <Text>Clay holds a magnifying glass over the mushroom. Through the lens, we see the ice crystals vibrating.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="01dc0a29-8536-4212-b70d-94cd5bb2b3d4">
      <Text>Clay</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="99878c55-5ab1-417c-86ed-2b8188952696">
      <Text>The sun comes out. What happens to ice when it gets warm?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="7ff9fc85-02b2-4904-b552-baac60bf3d10">
      <Text>Kids (V.O.)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="620be97d-9011-4899-bf59-3fb7c1129f83">
      <Text>It melts!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="809fb7b4-f4ea-49ce-8c42-133cef18507a">
      <Text>CLAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="dc101aee-e82f-4ed6-b86d-acdf6ec6e34c">
      <Text>It melts. It becomes... liquid! We’re going to follow the liquid trail to the Crystal Caves. Don’t forget your Moonie-Walkie-Talkie.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="1dd81c86-a240-4877-beb7-aba2bee5f45d">
      <Text>Stardust and Rocket get out their moon-shaped </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">walkie-talkies</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading" id="572a8b88-7eee-4c4e-9d80-0a5772b88fa5">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="15" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="CLAY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text Style="Bold+AllCaps">Back to the Room - ContINUOUS</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="94fc86e9-e7f3-4f8e-9e9e-31eabd66c5f9">
      <Text>Ray’s eyes widen. A spark of desperate inspiration hits her. She bolts upright and sprints towards the door.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="70f697d1-b00b-4944-8e80-d31cdffce46d">
      <Text>Clay (O.S.)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="cf9e3a08-9d04-49a2-8f9f-012ef272ffa2">
      <Text>Ready to explore?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading" id="f773e2eb-248d-45fa-bf85-ba07128c8444">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="15" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RAY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text Style="Bold+AllCaps">Ext. Kwan’s Apartment - Moments Later</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="61209150-25f6-4ad4-ab87-a7593a8e83bf">
      <Text>Ray reaches into the car backseat, and pulls out a special-edition Moonie-walkie from a box. She faces the camera.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="72189d55-c75f-40e8-bd7f-bc28b63e7516">
      <Text>RAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="63379a7b-9934-4478-8747-ab00203f0e13">
      <Text>Ready to explore...</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading" id="1eff6282-ac5e-46a0-b4e8-22eba9ef111a">
      <SceneProperties Length="3/8" Page="15" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RAY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text Style="Bold+AllCaps">Int. Kwan’s Apartment - Moments Later</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="afc3b86b-bab1-488e-b28b-70d935d44116">
      <Text>Ray returns to the sofa, clutching the walkie, turning a dial. The show’s theme wheezes out of its speaker. Her eyes lock on the TV. The upbeat theme plays over the credits. The names scroll by: Created by River Matthews &amp; Schuyler Park.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="30d2ef2c-79c5-4893-ad67-0d6ef390ac7b">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="f1a3235e-7b6a-4402-9788-8eeb82b04eeb">
      <Text>Ray to Clay. We’re going to the art fair. And we’re leaving with a job.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="e38a1782-03c9-4778-99a8-ede0aa018e7b">
      <Text>She sets the walkie down on a table, next to her termination letter.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Center" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.00" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="End of Act" id="8320508a-6b7a-43cd-9457-386c90d1a8a4">
      <Text>End of Act One</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="New Act" id="5c35dcaa-2ec2-4fa8-8d6f-44932370d5c7">
      <Text>Act Two</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading" id="675615da-4ed8-41f6-83e8-499f72b21ba2">
      <SceneProperties Length="3" Page="16" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="AUDIENCE">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="HANDLER">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="KIDS">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="KWAN">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RAY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RIVER">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text Style="Bold+AllCaps">Int. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Style="Bold+AllCaps">MSU</Text>
      <Text Style="Bold+AllCaps"> UNION - DAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="670467f0-4622-48c9-89a6-68c1dd08de61">
      <Text>On stage, </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">Stardust puppet</Text>
      <Text> pops up. Underneath, River puppeteers her while holding a microphone in the other hand.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="793f6ae1-88a4-4b28-891f-a9824fbcade0">
      <Text>RivER</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="4eb2e62d-b7b1-4bb6-8862-7d39a15ad1b1">
      <Text>Twinkle! Welcome, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">stardusters</Text>
      <Text>, to the art fair! I’m River Matthews.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical" id="aff691d5-ac62-4658-b871-9ebb45b744d9">
      <Text>(mic to Stardust)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="bd860cbc-b0b9-4b16-8603-1371d7f55903">
      <Text>And I’m your best friend, Stardust! Thanks for inviting us to be the 2025 Master of Ceremony! How long ago has it been since Stardust and us last saw you? How many years?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="31f1b7c3-57a9-4cf8-9b43-59b69e82108a">
      <Text>Audience</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="59b8a152-2c3e-4758-a099-f8884463cd43">
      <Text>Twenty! Nineteen! Years! Long time!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="68c78d46-e3c5-42c9-9c2b-6869583888d2">
      <Text>The ballroom is a maze of folding tables.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="b8301d16-0c2c-4bb1-a683-014604631268">
      <Text>RiVER (V.O.)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="4eb2e62d-b7b1-4bb6-8862-7d39a15ad1b1">
      <Text>Twenty years since we blasted off. But look at you all, it’s like we never left the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">Miniverse</Text>
      <Text>. Now, we landed on your world to celebrate the magic of discovery, beauty of the cosmos, and of course, the... </Text>
      <Text Style="Italic">Stardust</Text>
      <Text> that makes us, us!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="68c78d46-e3c5-42c9-9c2b-6869583888d2">
      <Text>Nearby, a paper on a music stand reads: $20 Autographs &amp; Photos with River Matthews and Stardust.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="56814fdb-261b-49f4-ada1-0f0952cb0132">
      <Text>River (V.O.)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="1c4ce236-5e49-4103-b1c5-73ce86e16a5c">
      <Text>Stardust hopes to meet every human on Earth. For autographs, we’ve got all the ink in the Solar System! Got enough smiles to go round? Twinkle, twinkle, twinkle!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="7401c963-125b-4377-844a-b623a723adfb">
      <Text>The line is a slow-moving herd of </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">kids </Text>
      <Text>and </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">parents</Text>
      <Text>. Ray stands with Kwan near the front, vibrating with manic energy.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="f3005305-fbd1-4aa1-908b-14390ba125db">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical" id="f9b9ce46-88e3-4258-a529-12de398079ca">
      <Text>(to camera)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="ea0ea29a-ee6c-4426-a8b2-251e71c2bce5">
      <Text>Many bring cookies. Some fan art. I bring the future. Cardstock, double-sided.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="3119994c-ee67-4752-9db3-9a17b896aef7">
      <Text>Ray pulls out her </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">resume</Text>
      <Text>. The font is </Text>
      <Text Size="10">tiny</Text>
      <Text> and </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">aggressive</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="93db4529-807c-417a-abf0-63f04ac5d5d3">
      <Text>A </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">toddler</Text>
      <Text> wearing a glittery star hat looks at Ray funny. Ray levels with the Toddler and raises her hand for a high five.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="356c280d-95d4-4e84-8472-d70da6bcf3bd">
      <Text>RAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="ad296d16-47e8-4705-8a8b-b583bc829840">
      <Text>Up high, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">starduster</Text>
      <Text>!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="0bc29dd8-8de7-4af2-9c84-90f5df463a98">
      <Text>The Toddler hides behind their parent. Ray lowers her hand.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="36f21cc3-d06e-46f8-b185-f6a4db291d70">
      <Text>RAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical" id="bdac4cb0-ce02-46df-9cb8-8090a7271aa5">
      <Text>(to camera)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="7bf2ffa8-e736-4970-af83-1da57043713e">
      <Text>This room’s a downer...</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="c3c1e345-7646-4153-9005-7aafd79ad318">
      <Text>A </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">kid</Text>
      <Text> walks by with an autographed drawing of a smiling sun.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="dc22ff15-3b5b-48a3-93d1-1579bd3d7797">
      <Text>RAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="606bc15d-0bb4-4493-aced-42481195d765">
      <Text>The sun’s actually white. It looks yellow due to Rayleigh scattering-</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="b4042697-e894-4199-89e6-c1520929e6ab">
      <Text>The Kid’s smile vanishes. They tear the paper into pieces.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="d911ea2f-19fc-4781-a515-ed9bafb832d2">
      <Text>KwaN</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="d40c7cb5-e3fb-419d-a1f2-78b3a8263b9d">
      <Text>No one else here’s your brother. There’s no need to traumatize them.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="c7a09412-6c36-4dee-852e-c02e376715bb">
      <Text>At the table, River</Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps"> </Text>
      <Text>signs away, looking up to</Text>
      <Text Size="10"> </Text>
      <Text>see</Text>
      <Text Size="10"> </Text>
      <Text>a</Text>
      <Text Size="10"> </Text>
      <Text>disheveled Ray and Kwan’s fixed stare. A </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">handler</Text>
      <Text> blocks the view.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="76008a05-aaa5-47f1-b058-711fa01aadf5">
      <Text>Handler</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="b861dd08-49e6-4836-b509-5b580941a924">
      <Text>Keep paths clear. Twenty bucks</Text>
      <Text Size="10"> </Text>
      <Text>ready-</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="5fd42846-dc70-4e25-8940-0470276e8b84">
      <Text>Ray opens her wallet, seeing only Canadian twenty-dollar bills. She sighs. Kwan nabs her bills and holds them up.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="54da0b23-ce8c-4ed2-8dbf-c74769b24f55">
      <Text>The Handler sees the colorful money and let's out</Text>
      <Text Size="10"> </Text>
      <Text>a</Text>
      <Text Size="10"> </Text>
      <Text>dry</Text>
      <Text Size="10"> </Text>
      <Text>laugh.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="80ffbe7e-6c09-4201-bbf8-6a76f2e7edf3">
      <Text>Handler</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="ac41c8ea-2cc0-423f-bb4b-ced974867290">
      <Text>This with y’all’s Monopoly money!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="8a7c20e7-e443-4627-a7c6-01818f1373a4">
      <Text>They gesture the siblings forward.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="c725ccec-ae06-460c-8baf-73e6e19b0e3b">
      <Text>RAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="f4dd4369-abbf-4512-8391-3376079c0391">
      <Text>River! Kwan and I miss you and uh-</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="a21fa2e0-d756-473d-9a06-34cb543d0821">
      <Text>RIVER</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="89611159-a65d-4f33-a28d-edb60c260577">
      <Text>That’s lovely, dear. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">Gotta</Text>
      <Text> twenty?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="525ca29f-936d-4484-b34d-690d0e0b1e07">
      <Text>Ray reaches into her pocket.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="f9a9ed8f-8ffe-479b-ab6d-3394e3709931">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="dae423b4-332f-433d-91ad-a488821986e7">
      <Text>Before exploring, we need our </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">walki</Text>
      <Text>-</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="525ca29f-936d-4484-b34d-690d0e0b1e07">
      <Text>River’s hand slips into the Stardust puppet on the table.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="35659586-e6f3-445f-a5c6-ffe96a29f2e1">
      <Text>River</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="ca453836-0d6b-4810-950b-91067437719f">
      <Text>Twinkle </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">twinkle</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">twinkle</Text>
      <Text>, kid! On another planet, everything is free. But here on Earth, stars like</Text>
      <Text Size="10"> </Text>
      <Text>bills!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="9d798026-ce58-4d16-b7d3-5e0da998ab88">
      <Text>The Stardust puppet eats the Canadian bill in Kwan’s hand.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="6f9d926d-97bb-41e4-9d63-7d3c1e50101e">
      <Text>River</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="94abcf3d-6020-4abb-8b1f-e58d9b16e14b">
      <Text>Stardust does not discriminate on race, gender, origin, social class! I eat any bill! Now, what would you like autographed?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="f0f4143e-c93e-4453-8ffd-93456bf3f4e6">
      <Text>Ray sets down her resume. River autographs it without a second thought. She passes back the resume back to Ray.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="d14e8796-a3eb-42f6-986d-c9856861c223">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="a013008c-fa31-42de-95c4-411adf4ad02f">
      <Text>You ain’t looking where ya signing?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="50d641fc-033c-4e15-931b-be31af8eaabb">
      <Text>RiVER</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="b0bd71dc-fb2d-4a48-8b48-cba135e20cee">
      <Text>Your menu looks nice, but we’re not hungry. Wanna photo?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="49b8d960-bed1-46c7-8a14-32e0df4f7cb6">
      <Text>In line, the </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">kids</Text>
      <Text> impatiently start chanting.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="048a1979-5dcc-41ea-a9ab-669fb4f0b2db">
      <Text>Kids</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="e7f72cda-b0b1-44d1-8d4b-2687ae72ccc2">
      <Text>Me! I wanna picture! Me! Me!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="07572e33-9775-4a43-9c28-1a0c2302baf4">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="961af308-10d8-42e5-9caa-753e76680f02">
      <Text>Trust me you don’t.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="7a7cc1fe-c025-4230-a467-12a42a9d98b5">
      <Text>Kids</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="f7461c96-c62c-46a6-9161-35ba43e6f9d2">
      <Text>We don’t... trust you...</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="403128d7-70cc-4c6f-9459-0af96944fa85">
      <Text>The Handler takes Kwan’s phone and their bills. They snap a picture of River, her puppet, smiling Kwan, and annoyed Ray.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="c0db62f4-7a21-4b59-a8a1-7b3922547f91">
      <Text>River pulls her hand out of the puppet. She</Text>
      <Text Size="10"> </Text>
      <Text>clocks</Text>
      <Text Size="10"> </Text>
      <Text>the</Text>
      <Text Size="10"> </Text>
      <Text>camera.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="26b08b67-7150-4589-8f36-7f17cda0993a">
      <Text>RIVER</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="4ed07b5f-08bb-40d5-a6c2-58338d71894c">
      <Text>No need to beef. Next, please.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="dfb8ed09-4eca-4917-a769-7f8ddbd951e1">
      <Text>Ray distances herself from River as she continues signing autographs and taking photos with fans. Ray points to River.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="cce0fdf1-a078-443d-9e5a-41f50d58fb32">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical" id="65cee874-2095-42a2-85c9-e2677e6719b0">
      <Text>(to camera)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="7ee19104-8ff7-487c-b3fa-bf2dca4c9f73">
      <Text>How would you describe this person? Nuh uh. She’s a...</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical" id="7978e1f8-772d-43d5-ae6a-9a3d86703fc5">
      <Text>(Holding her ear)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="b6b61f47-9c07-403a-8765-57c6f2d21db2">
      <Text>That’s right! A jerk! A piece of </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">sh</Text>
      <Text>-</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="f7af6cfb-1628-4e7d-b0a4-17e11c6b0742">
      <Text>KwAN</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="bdc2269c-7ecc-47ec-96db-8c617438d9cb">
      <Text>Shh... Hold your peace! The kids don’t </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">needa</Text>
      <Text> hear that negativity.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="c14eab9e-1375-45e4-a6d7-b0cbff9fef47">
      <Text>RAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="31a3e3e8-7deb-42e4-b3e1-907003f1b016">
      <Text>Kids deserve the truth, bruh.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading" id="897fe85c-dc2b-47a5-a45f-bf585eef6dd4">
      <SceneProperties Length="7/8" Page="19" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="KWAN">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RAY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="SKYE">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text Style="Bold+AllCaps">Ext. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Style="Bold+AllCaps">MSu</Text>
      <Text Style="Bold+AllCaps"> Union - Moments LATER</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="c159608c-2c52-4857-951f-1d5d9621b9c9">
      <Text>Ray and Kwan head outside. Ray is trembling from humiliation, holding the walkie. Her resume flies out of her hand.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="79ab00c2-972c-4bc9-b6fc-339ea66006aa">
      <Text>Schuyler “Skye” Park (51, confident) catches Ray’s resume before it flies away. They read.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="b66eb267-2e60-4b01-a5e4-1d791ad10a3a">
      <Text>SkYE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="99b5a1df-298f-40fc-b655-8cf2e6e09d42">
      <Text>Impressive menu selection... and an autograph from my best </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">frien</Text>
      <Text>-</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="e1ed820c-4e34-4346-bb2d-f2c4955bc268">
      <Text>Ray glares at the camera before snatching back her resume.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="de01257c-23d9-43c7-b27c-c22713da557e">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="66248bdb-aa42-4c5c-9da7-4555921a78c7">
      <Text>Stardust is everyone’s best friend.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="e007404d-ddc6-4fb1-a7fd-f504ee92b182">
      <Text>SkYE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="f20d6d1a-f338-45b4-aa0b-9945490807d6">
      <Text>But seriously your resume’s missing “Ray, </Text>
      <Text Style="Italic">Plasma with the Facts</Text>
      <Text> host.”</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="23ec6590-46c4-4a8a-84f6-c491c0045241">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="e87f7e58-45f7-4616-9246-2a80d09697ce">
      <Text>You’re subscribed to my channel?!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="0ed72db2-7b18-41a7-8c37-47e1bbdb13be">
      <Text>SKYE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="eb46994e-105e-4595-aaed-5dd71eb47f3a">
      <Text>I’ve seen all your episodes. The one about entropy had me fired up.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="58f679e4-a797-46a4-8ecb-ec26499d64fe">
      <Text>KWAN</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="72440e3a-ff9a-44f1-85d1-0ae757974335">
      <Text>Surprised you got fans in the wild-</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="496363bf-92fe-47a3-81c3-cd2afca10ee5">
      <Text>SkyE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="0fe27012-aaa4-49da-bbd8-b5c5eb3c690a">
      <Text>Watcha holding?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="2d146667-e218-479d-aa70-1e9624f5148f">
      <Text>Ray stows away the walkie in her clothes.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="f34df959-1016-4244-b97e-ec95974bf3bb">
      <Text>SkYE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="eb46994e-105e-4595-aaed-5dd71eb47f3a">
      <Text>Emotional baggage, huh? Look, I’ve </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">gotta</Text>
      <Text> run. But if you wanna answer my question, River and I will be at The Peanut Barrel tonight.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="5e9d0d17-29bf-45d1-bde1-fe9d4f06e434">
      <Text>Skye walks away. Ray gives a perplexed look at the camera.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading" id="9c2bdf4e-9fcf-4eb8-8db9-b3039f7cf7c5">
      <SceneProperties Length="2 3/8" Page="19" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="KWAN">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RAY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RAY &amp; KWAN">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RIVER">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="SKYE">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text Style="Bold+AllCaps">EXT. THE PEANUT BARREL - NIGHT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="1c0e0372-683b-464a-bc4e-446ef84da2f3">
      <Text>Ray and Kwan get out of the car and step onto the wood patio.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="5cef3d34-a74f-4c51-ba18-157638563451">
      <Text>At a corner table, Skye is laughing. Beside them sits River. Without the table between her and her fans, she seems human. Skye spots Ray and Kwan. River looks up and recognizes them.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="General" id="b47d93b7-6d8e-4734-8c84-09aae6d12f9b">
      <DualDialogue>
        <SpellCheckIgnoreLists>
          <IgnoredRanges/>
          <IgnoredWords/>
        </SpellCheckIgnoreLists>
        <Paragraph Type="Character" id="50c8917d-5d36-438c-a858-0eb83db7d608">
          <Text>Skye</Text>
        </Paragraph>
        <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="7a6e1897-db86-466d-b03c-acb5914e0e16">
          <Text>Welcome to planet peanut!</Text>
        </Paragraph>
        <Paragraph Type="Character" id="79a41286-44e0-49be-8c3d-7db180bd49f5">
          <Text>RIVER</Text>
        </Paragraph>
        <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="772436ea-f005-4624-9272-4334ed016a0a">
          <Text>The Canadians...</Text>
        </Paragraph>
      </DualDialogue>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="30b8b889-6adb-4244-9ede-02a0ae0c4d39">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="eca26361-2022-4784-a7c7-463458c6ca16">
      <Text>Skye mentioned cheap burgers here.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="f8621635-e0bb-499d-af2a-4f030791ed5d">
      <Text>Skye</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="3f0f9fcc-4676-4edf-a6cd-d14bcf6b0022">
      <Text>Please take a seat, unless you’re allergic to nuts </Text>
      <Text Style="Italic">like us</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="5aa91682-9609-491d-9c1d-461c4d7bb55c">
      <Text>Ray and Kwan sit. Kwan traces the deep grooves in the table.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="2fe88786-ede7-45f5-af25-2d8a82f767c5">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="c2e8b4fb-de52-4c53-9cbc-5024bb4c6911">
      <Text>Sorry about earlier. I’m just... an actor in transition.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="5e4a36cb-8114-4d2b-9578-36e7ccd029ba">
      <Text>RivER</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="05704165-b0d2-49f9-9595-4f5773d96b4c">
      <Text>Wow. Actor-speak for “I set something on fire.”</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="e5b2ce47-041f-445d-8623-fee463fc52ef">
      <Text>Skye</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="b71d1fa0-8c57-457d-bc89-02ac5d791b0d">
      <Text>No one knows </Text>
      <Text Style="Italic">washed up</Text>
      <Text> more than</Text>
      <Text Size="10"> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">Riv</Text>
      <Text>-</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="a29ec014-f838-460c-ba18-3ba5c02cff3f">
      <Text>River slaps Skye’s shoulder.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="60594f7a-6160-475f-b549-abdeb85fe248">
      <Text>KwaN</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="398a6586-cdbb-46a2-a1e2-56bfae8c1618">
      <Text>You sound familiar...</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="e063b385-df92-4776-adaf-5f259dc68350">
      <Text>River</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="b04359a9-35ae-4f76-9295-49156e4d1ec0">
      <Text>I voiced Stardust while Skye was the voice of the entire universe.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="6a58c1e7-e338-4108-a4e1-6438596a87fd">
      <Text>Ray &amp; Kwan</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="f163d35c-f1b4-400b-ac52-11242cd4dd03">
      <Text>Rocket? Rover? Robot? Satellite?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="89fa05b2-fb4d-4f1c-97b6-ff8eefd25c43">
      <Text>Skye</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="cd6b7184-5e44-4a84-b50f-61d23d047674">
      <Text>Guilty on all counts. Though the credits say “Schuyler Park,” I’ve been deconstructing since then.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="f5d4e848-5259-4af7-9957-85aeb9dcf43e">
      <Text>Skye shows a side-by-side post on a phone: a male-presenting actor from 2006 versus their current vibrant non-binary self.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="49a20313-d86c-490f-a278-184438ab3dd5">
      <Text>Skye</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="16986dae-0b1b-4f19-9d5e-134711d98847">
      <Text>I’m not the only “special edition” here. You got the stuff?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="d0020b84-51b9-4bcf-aaa1-349d9832e1d7">
      <Text>Ray sets the walkie on the table as a peace offering.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="048998b4-9e55-4eb3-a5e0-50cac5f7989b">
      <Text>KwAN</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="690ff235-73ce-476b-a13e-ce65f2bc2f1c">
      <Text Style="Italic">You’re giving yours away?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="595d630e-f322-4d2d-b30f-d4de9ca5754d">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="7c2055aa-33c4-4948-a1e1-5d45b64325d8">
      <Text>Shush. You still have yours.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="22f423f1-e03a-403e-9f5d-1424632f728c">
      <Text>River</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="c605a6e0-a5ad-4b46-a619-44df3001e027">
      <Text>Wow... The Moonie-Walkie-Talkie?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="fe778324-72e1-495e-ae48-6777397e3071">
      <Text>SkyE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="6423079a-0d8d-48b4-a24e-dba9131bc06a">
      <Text>Only a handful were manufactured.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="General" id="99d28227-4a16-4c1f-a4fd-4f7e1b4373a2">
      <DualDialogue>
        <SpellCheckIgnoreLists>
          <IgnoredRanges/>
          <IgnoredWords/>
        </SpellCheckIgnoreLists>
        <Paragraph Type="Character" id="bf29ac7b-aea4-4188-9dde-ee1d1586693b">
          <Text>River</Text>
        </Paragraph>
        <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="f2a4cead-a9b8-47d9-bc66-1c18f682633a">
          <Text>None of the crew got one.</Text>
        </Paragraph>
        <Paragraph Type="Character" id="17d3b0bf-de35-43ec-9d81-63336142b580">
          <Text>Skye</Text>
        </Paragraph>
        <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="c0c2e3e6-ab14-46b3-8589-8eea3be5ef78">
          <Text>They threw every prop away.</Text>
        </Paragraph>
      </DualDialogue>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="ebfcbe13-110b-4823-a544-35884d2dbfe8">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="578939e4-679a-436a-85d2-b0e3ab602eb3">
      <Text>My dad dumpster dives. He found it outside your studio and kept it, knowing how obsessed I was with your show. It’s been my north star.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="06e1c292-5374-4ba7-9f21-b05083b3e5a8">
      <Text>RiVER</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="6cc743b0-07c4-42ac-b118-31ab6c47da28">
      <Text>Well, “I’m super glad we’re forever buddies. Thanks for listening.”</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="e9a49aa4-2eaa-40c0-b389-2df2f4b0c556">
      <Text>River puts the walkie to her face and wells up.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="c8b89c2a-0e6e-472c-8a9f-f8eef5193ba3">
      <Text>KwaN</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical" id="8fa9e55b-5ed4-49be-b8bd-8529b0268d60">
      <Text>(in Tagalog; subtitled)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="1bd3fd97-e8d5-4415-b874-77905215ce0a">
      <Text>She is not fit to walkie-talkie.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="b79a04d7-e36c-4fce-a1dc-2b0c0bc4fbeb">
      <Text>RaY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical" id="9df1dc3b-af44-4301-bdbf-6468645e8765">
      <Text>(in Tagalog; subtitled)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="96c2a1b9-a186-4b31-8506-5ece7e61db2a">
      <Text>Shut up, Kwan.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="4e911f10-4bc2-4f34-bf8f-0c45cc16fc85">
      <Text>River</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="ece0afce-1527-4a82-a6d6-df2966a6de91">
      <Text>Tagalog? Stardust is very popular in the Philippines, so the studio provided us the best translators.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="8722891a-2fdd-41c0-a8e8-e9ecf60d67a9">
      <Text>RaY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="d293a76d-db16-4f79-a59f-8f5228b92202">
      <Text>Is </Text>
      <Text Style="Italic">Titi</Text>
      <Text> the space beetle also called </Text>
      <Text Style="Italic">Titi</Text>
      <Text> over there-?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="6e236169-f218-4897-9fbc-b147d66b8d32">
      <Text>KwAN</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="6e0e3f1a-2a66-4e84-90f4-92bd499bc80f">
      <Text Style="Italic">Titi</Text>
      <Text> like in penis-</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="dff5a528-3fbf-4991-8431-815192ba7f78">
      <Text>River</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical" id="4fd58be9-3128-4c55-9592-defac4d51be1">
      <Text>(in</Text>
      <Text Size="10"> </Text>
      <Text>bad</Text>
      <Text Size="10"> </Text>
      <Text>Tagalog;</Text>
      <Text Size="10"> </Text>
      <Text>subtitled)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="f494286e-8bb6-40a5-96df-b38c98e43956">
      <Text>I’m super glad we’re friends. Thanks for listening. I’ll take your menu- resume off your hands.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="ef0b7665-e8c0-4655-aa06-d655d0f0f9c2">
      <Text>Ray takes out the crumbled resume and hands it to River, feeling the weight of the moment. Her objective is done.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="12abd3be-70cc-49f2-959d-c1750d619de9">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="f64eb329-2317-4a66-8352-075b632c43aa">
      <Text>Well, bruh, time to get you crying once you see that video in the car.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="fd1964e7-a3a0-4a07-befb-8638e6dd5763">
      <Text>River</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="5ad288fd-a6c7-4370-81da-2b5254947e78">
      <Text>Get home safe cause... there will be a future for stardust like us.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="f28147db-7ef5-4167-875b-d81a1b239c9d">
      <Text>Ray looks puzzled. Is that a promise? River opens her arms. As Ray steps forward, her hand brushes the walkie. Her thumb finds the dial and switches it over to </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">record</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="51274ae5-6a7c-477c-bbdf-00a913e340fa">
      <Text>RAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="e497a875-eb6e-4504-8a79-179b039685ab">
      <Text>Looking forward to hearing more...</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="fb4cb628-c16d-4956-95e7-91d62532b94d">
      <Text>Ray sinks into the hug, holding the creator of her childhood to absorb some of that old magic. She smiles at the camera.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading" id="d1d50a89-a49e-4458-98b9-c88c8f35ddf3">
      <SceneProperties Length="3/8" Page="22" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="CLAY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="KWAN">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RAY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text Style="Bold+AllCaps">Int. Ray’s Car - MomentS LATER</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="7c663946-221b-4bb4-951a-5b6fae956cae">
      <Text>Ray drives through the dark streets. In the passenger seat, Kwan watches Clay’s message on her phone with teary eyes.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="b551088d-8866-4b37-80a4-ce06836ea7f1">
      <Text>CLAY (O.S.)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="df66aad8-99a1-4d11-b218-b3815e2df6c9">
      <Text>...ever you’re doing, it’s working.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="3a2728fd-fc38-46f0-8c98-caa888a89b50">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="c08aa477-d50f-476d-9d5c-a8faa2397ea8">
      <Text>Bruh. Can I borrow your walkie?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="edc58aca-3e6c-42c0-9fdc-4712d016708e">
      <Text>KwAN</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="dacdac33-4398-44ff-9a09-f9c6a2a4480b">
      <Text>Already miss it?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading" id="269e2b51-6e11-4c72-ad2b-95b805c7d751">
      <SceneProperties Length="3/8" Page="22" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RIVER">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="SKYE">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text Style="Bold+AllCaps">Int. Kwan’s Apartment - Night</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="cfa84350-1c4e-4e36-b0bb-d305b9a42580">
      <Text>Ray lies on the sofa, then gets out Kwan’s walkie. She taps </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">play</Text>
      <Text>. The audio is layered with clatters of silverware.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="ed383739-7aa6-457b-9c4d-63ac2cfc977c">
      <Text>SkYE (V.O.)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="96eba855-c18e-4f14-900a-08bbce5c8fe4">
      <Text>The kids may be grown up, but Stardust is still in their hearts.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="4a0a8fcd-7c0c-4dda-a99a-2a45dcba0dbb">
      <Text>River (V.O.)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="67888961-08bc-43b0-89a5-98296734898a">
      <Text>And Stardust and her sister will reach the next generation.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="d7a5ab92-22a2-47a5-9b35-e639f497306b">
      <Text>SkYE (V.O.)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="5aabf05b-41d7-4245-ba53-cf7a34f6a8cb">
      <Text>We’re in the green?!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading" id="269e2b51-6e11-4c72-ad2b-95b805c7d751">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="22" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RIVER">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text Style="Bold+AllCaps">Int. The Peanut Barrel - Night (Flashback)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="6c820dd8-7f7f-48d3-966a-cc7d0d1fab52">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Style="AllCaps">StarPower</Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps"> puppet</Text>
      <Text>, a pink axolotl, is in River’s hand.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="2668d376-837e-45cc-92f8-3ed66c8a864e">
      <Text>RIVER</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="7edb4c0f-2e3e-47b2-abf6-6b2a8ddbcbaa">
      <Text Style="Italic">Pink</Text>
      <Text> actually. I got the call today- The network gave us the greenlight, Skye. We’re back in business. </Text>
      <Text Style="Italic">Stardust</Text>
      <Text> is getting a revival and will feature her sister, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">StarPower</Text>
      <Text>!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading" id="2e197cba-7e2c-4484-abb3-0b9f01ef6da3">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="22" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="SKYE">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text Style="Bold+AllCaps">Int. Kwan'S APARTMENT - ConTINUOUS</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="0aa6e50e-6a9e-4a2a-bf1d-9d8a6d631a74">
      <Text>Ray gives a hopeful look at the camera.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="27ef10cf-2245-4348-a349-02b23dec5a1d">
      <Text>SkYE (V.O.)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="7c9b611a-3270-4888-9cfe-392039511815">
      <Text>I love that axolotl. Glad our autograph tour won’t be in vain.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading" id="269e2b51-6e11-4c72-ad2b-95b805c7d751">
      <SceneProperties Length="5/8" Page="23" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RIVER">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="SKYE">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text Style="Bold+AllCaps">Int. The Peanut Barrel - Night (Flashback)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="05f89c99-e42a-49d7-a4eb-c23f1bdff3d4">
      <Text>River throws her arms out with joy finally breaking through.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="35962260-2526-4a10-a797-1da8f59e1689">
      <Text>SKYE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="5af55dcb-5e80-42eb-995d-57f2af332b43">
      <Text>But, there’s pain in my veins...</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="75d95930-d023-4112-aa87-110366cca12b">
      <Text>RiVER</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="3a6033d8-8590-4e93-8380-4e3aee8e749b">
      <Text>You don’t seem excited?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="a6fb40e2-c501-467c-b27e-c506f8baa816">
      <Text>SkYE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="69fc31fa-a9a3-4292-991c-85c16eb1a98e">
      <Text>What about Clay? Would he be?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="ce8ce4ac-4572-4ada-a466-8d3c89f6dc28">
      <Text>The name hangs in the air like a cold front. River’s smile thins. She picks up a peanut and snaps the shell. </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">Crack</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="386e7e88-5817-4637-a997-fe9648709d83">
      <Text>RiVER</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="4eb5e0ac-30d0-481c-9aa7-3402c6b3b06e">
      <Text>We’re not asking Clay back.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="c79eee75-225b-454d-bfef-da5bc16f1ba4">
      <Text>She grabs a bag of peanuts and spills them across her plate.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="07723a29-f5f2-4e6a-ab9a-e8556d7929cc">
      <Text>SkYE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="789ee715-1751-4db9-83c0-d9e493d8c2d2">
      <Text>In 1999, we found Clay after a hundred auditions. This revival? It’ll be in the thousands.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="7fbfa379-a6e9-4922-9fd6-f36df86b4fdf">
      <Text>River</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="390a99d1-218b-4f2a-8c60-67bff29a0b52">
      <Text>And so we’ll sift through them all until we find the perfect peanut.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="38e1a125-f0cb-4010-bf8e-1a3186e7e058">
      <Text>River picks through the pile and holds up a flawless peanut.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading" id="2e197cba-7e2c-4484-abb3-0b9f01ef6da3">
      <SceneProperties Length="5/8" Page="23" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="KIDS">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RAY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RIVER">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="SKYE">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text Style="Bold+AllCaps">Int. Kwan'S APARTMENT - ConTINUOUS</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="9653f0da-dc0e-4e5e-9b51-862fbcdf0310">
      <Text>Ray sits upright, her eyes lighting up with a surge of hope.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="9446a3f2-71fe-4b8d-ad8d-919559edcde8">
      <Text>SkYE (V.O.)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="1c6c5715-af3c-490f-a20f-e6b9a139f07d">
      <Text>Actually, I think we just met our perfect candidate.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="0b8557bb-2b6e-40c9-b604-ee59d19ed1f5">
      <Text>River (V.O.)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="6cac7c1b-ad36-4516-9a2f-da0cc3ccf175">
      <Text>Nonsense. She’s completely unprofessional. The kids said it themselves. They don’t trust her.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="7a7cc1fe-c025-4230-a467-12a42a9d98b5">
      <Text>Kids (V.O.)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="db8b26ff-d999-4f98-8e6c-8c738802314e">
      <Text>We don’t... trust you...</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="cef4be4f-1e6c-4c40-9415-aad2a6ffe7b6">
      <Text>The light dies in Ray’s eyes. She stares coldly</Text>
      <Text Size="10"> </Text>
      <Text>at</Text>
      <Text Size="10"> </Text>
      <Text>the</Text>
      <Text Size="10"> </Text>
      <Text>camera.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="281c03ef-83a1-4108-9200-b58ff4405853">
      <Text>Skye (V.O.)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="d2716a8d-76c3-4668-b4c4-79261506428a">
      <Text>Don't write her off. Check out her channel first, “Plasma Facts.”</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="4ed62142-27a9-43dc-99fa-a778949f9e88">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="e252f41a-5ff1-42be-95ae-6f546d95f72b">
      <Text>“</Text>
      <Text Style="Italic">Plasma with the Facts</Text>
      <Text>.”</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="6ffe2fdc-8e8c-4217-b05f-2a65543ef85e">
      <Text>RiVER (V.O.)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="9df5dd0a-a7de-49c1-a4c6-02f556dcb947">
      <Text>I’ll deal with it in the morning. Based on her portfolio, Ray’s got </Text>
      <Text Style="Italic">Cat Scouts</Text>
      <Text> to fall back to.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading" id="2e14b9e4-f804-429a-9716-5529b9e32374">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="24" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="SKYE">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text Style="Bold+AllCaps">Int. The PeanUT BARREL - Night (Flashback)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="e5800021-da60-483a-aaf6-5aa392a9494b">
      <Text>River sets the walkie on her plate then Ray’s resume on top.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="57748337-93a7-442e-9a6c-fb3866d2855d">
      <Text>Skye</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="a4e46d9d-fe6c-4062-bd45-dd7602120d0b">
      <Text>You don’t want the walkie-talkie?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="26a1eb6a-506d-4492-b57d-3f23386fe2d1">
      <Text>River and Skye stand to leave.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="26a1eb6a-506d-4492-b57d-3f23386fe2d1">
      <Text>A waiter swoops in, clearing the check, dishes, and the toy.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading" id="d0fe1a09-444e-4f9b-a131-435795e3ac77">
      <SceneProperties Length="4/8" Page="24" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RAY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RIVER">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text Style="Bold+AllCaps">Int. Kwan’s Apartment - ConTINUOUS</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="d56e688d-28bf-452c-ade2-4d077453345a">
      <Text>Ray slumps back, deflated with a look of pure betrayal.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="3578044e-268a-4cf5-9f80-c849fc325968">
      <Text>River (V.O.)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="448276e2-9d5c-4ac4-a103-8b1ecfbb4028">
      <Text>It was a lovely gesture. But I’m done with this past.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="ab5b5181-ab71-4841-9d09-fc18106cc0bd">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="d5a527e6-e3ff-4a66-9fd3-09a633f7012e">
      <Text>Then why the hell are you bringing the show back?!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="42d784f5-25d4-4c91-a107-ff0c0a9abf97">
      <Text>Ray pauses the recording. She sits in the silence of the dark room for a moment before collapsing onto the sofa.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="2bc58307-e659-468d-9da8-c5ec7268d964">
      <Text>The door behind her is a bit ajar. Kwan has been listening.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="9bed0928-dc65-4651-a85d-bf51e1931b7f">
      <Text>Ray (O.S.)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="934c5e24-797d-4ee6-a791-6637c3a0cf2a">
      <Text>I can’t be helped... being professional all alone...</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading" id="fec7e765-439a-405a-a9b8-eab7a34cafe1">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="24" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats/>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text Style="Bold+AllCaps">Int. Kwan’s Bedroom</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="af41cf3d-9f38-46a2-a2f8-bd54c8482be1">
      <Text>Kwan looks through his shelf and spots an old dazzling envelop. He pulls it out and reads it.
- Date: July 11, 2009
- Sender: Clay, 42 Stardew Creek, Brooklyn, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">NY</Text>
      <Text> 11201.
- Receiver: Kwan Reyes, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">Corewell</Text>
      <Text> Health Butterworth Hospital, 100 Michigan St NE, Grand Rapids, MI 49503</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Center" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.00" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="End of Act" id="8320508a-6b7a-43cd-9457-386c90d1a8a4">
      <Text>End of Act Two</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="New Act" id="6b67055e-8e0a-4c01-b26e-48bdef828a9a">
      <Text>ACT Three</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading" id="8496ff4c-32e4-40f5-ab75-3d547697cbeb">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="25" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats/>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text Style="Bold+AllCaps">Ext. The PEANUT BARREL - Night</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="ead8481a-3387-401f-ac42-6adbc79e442f">
      <Text>The </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">dirty dumpsters</Text>
      <Text> behind the restaurant.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="9b9f4d36-f745-46c6-b3c5-2ef853064e88">
      <Text Style="AllCaps">Thump </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Style="AllCaps">thump</Text>
      <Text>. The lid swings open. Kwan pops out, covered in peanuts. He triumphantly holds up the walkie.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading" id="d0fe1a09-444e-4f9b-a131-435795e3ac77">
      <SceneProperties Length="7/8" Page="25" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="KWAN">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RAY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text Style="Bold+AllCaps">Int. Kwan’s Apartment - Morning</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="1b97fda1-dcfb-4077-b236-bc51222eef00">
      <Text>Ray sleeps on the sofa. The walkie near her activates.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="4f4e8d63-874e-4a86-aa7e-fabae87f7f25">
      <Text>Kwan (V.O.)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="f7404b00-4a5c-4873-b165-6ce0814db5f2">
      <Text>Captain Ray. Come in, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">sistuh</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="f1720952-7574-4a04-aa3a-2bc588ea1ee4">
      <Text>RAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical" id="e6e36ee5-6417-4f5a-901e-0903bf0f2a1e">
      <Text>(Slumping over)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="8dcd72c4-3dc1-4544-adda-07a9496b5504">
      <Text>Yo, this walkie-talkie got all the recordings since we were kids...</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="dee05ce4-357c-4f2d-ae19-1b25c0d674b9">
      <Text>KWAN (V.O.)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="cbb081e8-ecfa-4c27-b2fe-659a4a655571">
      <Text>This is the year 2025.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="abd0c44a-cfb7-4fd5-baa2-71466119979a">
      <Text>Ray activates the walkie.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="06563f06-0b61-4dce-9884-fc65d0e99529">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="b6964e86-12ca-4696-9a29-5d40094e3b1f">
      <Text>Captain Kwan. You got a third walkie I never knew about or did you... dumpster dive? You listened in on me listening in on to River and Skye’s conservation?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="6f2df3b4-f5c3-41b1-bf8d-c7e236b8982e">
      <Text>KWAN (V.O.)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="d3114923-f872-419b-be90-bf762f83bf80">
      <Text>Recording people without their permission is sorta illegal, </Text>
      <Text Style="Italic">bruh</Text>
      <Text>. River is right...</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="General" id="e597c7cb-7fb4-4ece-89d9-fc72991fc73c">
      <DualDialogue>
        <SpellCheckIgnoreLists>
          <IgnoredRanges/>
          <IgnoredWords/>
        </SpellCheckIgnoreLists>
        <Paragraph Type="Character" id="76bab34c-f7b0-4a8a-ad60-75ef47006db4">
          <Text>Ray</Text>
        </Paragraph>
        <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="19f7325b-bf11-40a6-947e-6f562e5cc6ce">
          <Text>I </Text>
          <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">aM</Text>
          <Text> </Text>
          <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">uNpRoFfEsSiOnAl</Text>
          <Text>.</Text>
        </Paragraph>
        <Paragraph Type="Character" id="ffc0f416-e893-4144-a163-a3815e1526ad">
          <Text>KWAN (V.O.)</Text>
        </Paragraph>
        <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="ae13ddbd-9ae7-4263-b947-f4a91769803a">
          <Text>You are unprofessional.</Text>
        </Paragraph>
      </DualDialogue>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="88f5a741-d8a2-442c-ab87-cbdd2e02ff39">
      <Text>KwaN (V.O.)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="7db18b6a-5151-49a1-b6c5-926d62128243">
      <Text>It makes you fun! Also spontaneity! Sis, look extra good today. I’m taking you to another planet!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="2eb88d09-254c-46c4-a40b-74b446876190">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical" id="973084d1-1a40-474b-8f63-dbe63bbd81e1">
      <Text>(to camera)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="c4b97a80-50b9-4cdf-aaf5-36b52fa9c826">
      <Text>Do I or do I not look presentable? Be honest. I won’t bite... Wow, too honest- Well I’m no animal. I punch-</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="2c46332c-1f9a-45fe-aba8-0a047fbd0000">
      <Text>Ray is about to punch the camera.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading" id="8c859571-e764-4017-8af3-6e4234c3a39d">
      <SceneProperties Length="1 1/8" Page="26" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="KWAN">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RAY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text Style="Bold+AllCaps">Ext. Parking Lot - Day</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="63f4b1b9-53d6-4c5f-9453-b1c1ef594e98">
      <Text>Wearing her long sleeve and jeans, Ray walks out of the complex. She gets into the passenger side of Kwan’s car.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="b98235c0-200f-4995-bcc4-99f5319beb5e">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical" id="6bded0cd-1a4a-44d0-85b1-5bb0e9b7b231">
      <Text>(to camera)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="fc14184f-36eb-40f5-82be-cd29dfbfe27f">
      <Text>What planet are we visiting today? Hopefully not another rocky one-</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="6f692890-3db7-4cf1-9e37-5db4191cb68d">
      <Text>A pair of sock puppets, resembling Stardust on the left hand and Rocket on the right, pop up outside the passenger window.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="1613001a-0317-44d2-aa95-1dc63ca5994d">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="9ab0bfe3-2f14-40d2-bb55-d9121e12b94b">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">Ahhhhhhhh</Text>
      <Text>! A </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">socky</Text>
      <Text> planet!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="beeaa0a5-531c-49fd-a8b2-adbe16fe5e2a">
      <Text>Kwan zips around and gets in the driver’s seat.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="d7272f2e-62aa-4045-a66a-7db47ea1e567">
      <Text>Kwan</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical" id="941cc5d2-fbe5-4d3a-97af-1b54e16b5f05">
      <Text>(as Stardust)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="f5239f5d-b6db-41fb-97d4-1027823334ae">
      <Text>Twinkle, twinkle, twinkle!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="6a5d5868-a26b-4bc4-9240-16c1d9bb9538">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="c0572177-1942-4ed2-b49c-4c699e28f77c">
      <Text>Alright, where are we going you little star freak?!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="61f157af-a88e-40e4-800c-8f2ec4434b03">
      <Text>KWAN</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="9e930f49-19f5-4095-86b6-949cda0c4c8b">
      <Text>Twinkle, twinkle, twinkle.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="e34524f2-d34e-4326-8b87-c0b13406ae5d">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="0d35dcee-4c8a-416c-bec1-fbabeff0d0de">
      <Text>I never understand you. Maybe I should ask Rocket.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="7e4d84db-3b1b-4c0c-a307-2e282339b7d9">
      <Text>Kwan starts the car with the Rocket puppet on his right hand.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="d98e299c-2878-4be8-90a7-0f54909889eb">
      <Text>KwaN</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="a8b54e08-9323-4c33-a989-7b00c1b90dd8">
      <Text>I can’t hear you over my </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">thrusters</Text>
      <Text>!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="5f48e489-b87a-4391-8232-fd376bf63a33">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="3c79ff33-c46e-452d-8a7a-526b359f5549">
      <Text>Seriously, bruh. Where to?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="4819c16b-5da6-4d39-a070-3a145620d57d">
      <Text>KwAN</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="5b99e2a4-942c-4569-8a8a-0bef203a542c">
      <Text>To a potential mentor.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="942214f6-f023-4b85-9e62-60bbe4f0f069">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="bd3476bb-586b-43f7-b9dd-8dbda0aebedb">
      <Text>Don’t you have a mentor?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="a00ec8e8-fc1d-4b8b-85ca-9dcc93ec0c91">
      <Text>Kwan</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="b18f0a07-3ea0-4f2d-8145-b013c9b6a73b">
      <Text Style="Italic">Supervisor</Text>
      <Text> Dr. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">Zepf</Text>
      <Text>. I’d fall off the universe without her guidance.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="77eb5841-8888-4577-b84a-08b90f24aa25">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="99c8ef8a-139b-4495-919d-2d23730d4652">
      <Text>Is the new mentor </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">outta</Text>
      <Text> this world?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="3afb1379-2752-4e63-85c1-4b6065d20c91">
      <Text>KwAN</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="a62f3b05-d937-4901-9627-42afc82c7fe3">
      <Text>Out of this world is not far at all-</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="e66dda89-0db6-4c94-9a87-f92caa802e6e">
      <Text>Ray smirks at the camera.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Transition" id="6a282089-5460-4398-912f-3ee545591291">
      <Text>Jump cut to:</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading" id="be9e3c6b-bd52-4f37-b174-8ebf756e0d87">
      <SceneProperties Length="1 6/8" Page="27" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="KWAN">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RAY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text Style="Bold+AllCaps">Int. Kwan’s Car - Night</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="7c28d331-35ae-40f7-a37e-9e0d7c609d32">
      <Text>Ray is now asleep in the passenger seat. The sock puppets slitter around her left side. They startle her awake.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="72df0cbf-a7d1-4244-80d4-f8d1797ea66e">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="47c3db16-5b78-4209-9dda-58a98d871687">
      <Text>Bruh?! How long was I knocked out?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="d44cdf07-add4-4e0d-8033-1dc91af52962">
      <Text>KWAN</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="b5c617e9-5003-4bc7-8c77-58b8c3d29626">
      <Text>Ten hours, forty-eight minutes, and thirty-seven seconds. You’re so old-</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="b8bda20a-0d0b-4213-848d-cdcc3023cfdc">
      <Text>RaY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="c44de9bd-971e-4112-8fe8-0421d0a28a7f">
      <Text>I’m twenty-nine! And you said the surprise trip ain’t far nor long!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="61b343d8-f6cd-4e56-8556-c99f8b505b30">
      <Text>KwaN</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="2ae15135-052a-495f-8e35-bb50d30c04f7">
      <Text>Time is relative! And eleven hundred kilometers is nothing!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="e4cbafaa-ea67-4238-9438-6fb6fa07d820">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="90ae1337-fe3d-4ad8-83c2-413eb23d783b">
      <Text>That’s what I get for believing an </Text>
      <Text Style="Italic">astrophysicist</Text>
      <Text>... Wherever we are, we’ve got no relationship to...</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical" id="5c18cd67-06af-437a-be92-dd2f602e7bae">
      <Text>(to camera)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="517fe6c4-e8e9-4904-acca-253a74b57975">
      <Text>Where are we...? Ew, New Jersey?!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical" id="4bf54097-a3a2-4bf4-a93e-e64ad378c6c0">
      <Text>(Listening more intently)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="4c765433-ff29-4dbe-894c-31e959b9ccf3">
      <Text>Ah... New York City. Manhattan...? Ugh, Brooklyn.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical" id="b30fd531-e13a-4059-a148-fdb1aee4beb0">
      <Text>(to Kwan)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="a4fd7aea-1d00-4d9d-b720-5e58ed8d3fbc">
      <Text>Your potential mentor lives in NYC? Considering switching to Columbia?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="29e46160-8dea-440c-8216-5d0aff8c47a6">
      <Text>Kwan</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="5ce60a13-e6ae-47a4-a68b-8c56c0319589">
      <Text>Nope. Your potential mentor’s here.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="fc5f9479-0a13-4362-a8f3-84e0e46c82e6">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="d6eb7fd4-8be9-40fe-a9b9-2e0f42c8395b">
      <Text>I don’t get you. You think I </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">gotta</Text>
      <Text> shot on Broadway? If I didn’t make it in Toronto, NYC will crush me.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="f3d58200-0f32-4b19-8cf3-91912b92da66">
      <Text>KwAN</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="792a249a-c7fc-450a-a35d-c953914b9f3b">
      <Text>You won’t have to do this alone.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="b23f4fb9-f05f-4841-aef3-70f6a25630ba">
      <Text>RAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="7513b64c-44b0-4f3d-b7ea-676a38f80a26">
      <Text>Right. I have you, Stardust sock, Rocket sock to crash and burn with.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="0831e84b-4700-4db6-9f54-5e9ebaefbaf1">
      <Text>Kwan</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="f5d45b91-a175-4bd4-a65b-5f2e34da64ec">
      <Text>And Clay, the real deal.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="2a4f1458-cc66-4db1-b79e-47d08c314456">
      <Text>Kwan passes Clay’s envelop to Ray. He points to a brownstone apartment nearby. Ray looks at Kwan, terrified.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="34bf9eea-ecf2-4134-830f-477066c9edd4">
      <Text>Kwan</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="49f336af-7e23-4b03-b1f3-ecf66f77fa1c">
      <Text>Based on my calculations, Clay lives right there.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="27f9ec1a-ecf8-470b-bf9a-adeb7e9f3abd">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="e1b7cd5d-0045-4a91-920c-e5a9cc87964a">
      <Text>Oh no </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">no</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">no</Text>
      <Text>. I’m not bothering our lord and savior, Clay. No one can convince me- Bruh, watcha doing?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="852fe56d-43ed-4caf-b5b5-eb23b2f71cbe">
      <Text>Kwan, distracted on his phone, is now watching a silent and captioned YouTube video from...</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="d78adc4c-6cc3-449d-86c4-81034c75a79a">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="5eb312bd-4772-4b20-a3c5-4b748c991dba">
      <Text>Ms. Aurora...</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="210112b3-adde-486e-bea8-60892a6eee5a">
      <Text>Ray gets out of the car. She stands under a lit lamppost. She opens Clay’s letter, holds it up to the camera, then reads.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="2f96d2ea-c52d-49d8-923d-dffd10cbebff">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="c03e0b80-c509-4e1f-a152-e5b6c3fb7c09">
      <Text>Dear </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">starduster</Text>
      <Text> Kwan, thanks for writing. Hope the hospital is treating you to ice cream and cookies. You and your sister’s relationship may be ice cold now due to your firework accident. Just know, accidents happen. Stardust has accidentally set me on fire. She’s a star doing nuclear fusion after all. Don’t let Ray get you down. With fireballs, there are rays of sunshine ahead, kid. And you and your sis likes theatre? Me too! Maybe, I’ll catch the </Text>
      <Text Style="Italic">Kwan n’ Ray</Text>
      <Text> show someday. You look fabulous by the way. Whatever you’re doing, it’s working... Clear skies, Clay.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="edf3583a-f2e8-4640-bc42-26893b18fc3b">
      <Text>Ray looks up from Clay’s letter, welling up with tears.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading" id="4bb5a44f-1ad9-41ce-9bce-8db3af6e502c">
      <SceneProperties Length="1 1/8" Page="28" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="CLAY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RAY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RAY &amp; CLAY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text Style="Bold+AllCaps">Ext. Brooklyn Street - Day</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="1ccb20ca-0a12-40cb-8c2f-d3dd6a528596">
      <Text>A </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">sun-baked</Text>
      <Text> brownstone block is active with dog walkers.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="b2b6da71-53d7-43fd-8bc6-68622ecb3601">
      <Text>Kwan stands by his car, watching Ray approach an apartment. His phone buzzes. He anxiously reads the notification. </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">Urgent: Disciplinary Hearing - Misuse of Research Funds</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="b2b6da71-53d7-43fd-8bc6-68622ecb3601">
      <Text>Ray gives a thumbs up to Kwan, who nervously gives one back. She grits her teeth</Text>
      <Text Size="10"> </Text>
      <Text>to</Text>
      <Text Size="10"> </Text>
      <Text>the</Text>
      <Text Size="10"> </Text>
      <Text>camera.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="5c0d2bb6-78d9-4f45-ad6f-2ef9bb9a58ae">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="4a284e9d-9b6f-42ec-8143-46d6efc3dbe1">
      <Text>This is it. Where all states of matter align. Will he mentor me?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical" id="7edca389-4bdc-4e28-95f3-6f557118714f">
      <Text>(Pause)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="4a284e9d-9b6f-42ec-8143-46d6efc3dbe1">
      <Text Style="Italic">Maybe</Text>
      <Text>...? Will he tolerate me...?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical" id="45b87116-ffb2-4561-92f9-8a1a75a6dafd">
      <Text>(Taking offense)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="4a284e9d-9b6f-42ec-8143-46d6efc3dbe1">
      <Text>Okay, very funny.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="ad86a54a-3236-4a92-b702-334c95eef538">
      <Text>Ray approaches the front door and rings the doorbell.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="cb3d316c-dab5-479d-b192-b3e1a74d64bd">
      <Text Style="AllCaps">Ding dong</Text>
      <Text>. No answers. </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">Ding dong</Text>
      <Text>. Nada.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="18f737c0-a504-4e20-8a9d-c8cc5c0db960">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical" id="6012b405-2ddd-455c-b8fd-d271cf245d07">
      <Text>(to camera)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="b6d565f1-1353-4a46-ac05-d6c2e70d5618">
      <Text>Let’s do the Stardust knock! Would that be cheesy? Yes. </Text>
      <Text Style="Italic">It is cheesy</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="cb3d316c-dab5-479d-b192-b3e1a74d64bd">
      <Text>Ray knocks on the door in the Stardust rhythm.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="dad49f81-0a5e-4ec5-a390-26863b52c01b">
      <Text Style="AllCaps">Knock</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Style="AllCaps">knock</Text>
      <Text>... </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">knock</Text>
      <Text>, </Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">knock</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="e025ec4b-097c-4494-9a6b-e3c864145c70">
      <Text>ClAY (O.S.)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="e0671514-93b8-4d69-8254-5a595133e02b">
      <Text Style="AllCaps">Someone’s </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Style="AllCaps">freakin</Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">’ </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Style="AllCaps">knockin</Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">’?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="33812256-ff4e-45ae-b856-4ce87c49b34d">
      <Text>Ray &amp; Clay</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="af660f29-a43e-4816-ac29-14b6dbe2dee2">
      <Text Style="AllCaps">Someone’s </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Style="AllCaps">freakin</Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">’ </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Style="AllCaps">knockin</Text>
      <Text Style="AllCaps">’?
I wonder who’s on the dot</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="c67a8205-0caf-449d-bca7-11876d5c2d88">
      <Text>The door swings open to reveal Billy Clayton Dubois, now 46 and wearing a brown cap and stained hoodie.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="b2ecb31d-dfdd-4cbd-ae1c-d3a9db53e10f">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="58d626ce-affa-4e74-8702-f8f264161bf9">
      <Text>Clay... Stardust is in trouble and she needs your help. I need your help. We all need your help.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="125b2b44-d175-4f57-b835-fd528d2f3112">
      <Text>Ray proudly looks at the camera.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="9c0a60a4-dd7d-48ad-ba7e-91d74701a1de">
      <Text>ClAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="ae5d0567-52e7-497b-9219-69af7136ec33">
      <Text>You... It’s you.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="125b2b44-d175-4f57-b835-fd528d2f3112">
      <Text>Clay looks at the camera. He smiles then extends his hand out like he is offering a handshake. Then, he covers the camera.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Transition" id="bace9187-3110-4189-919e-6fb5b99363c6">
      <Text>Cut to black.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="d33813b2-74c6-4cc4-a187-8cdfe02f7c5c">
      <Text>ClAY (V.O.)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="a17de29b-f2bf-4a0a-aea8-1eb795c2140f">
      <Text>Do I look like I care?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Center" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.00" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="End of Act" id="8320508a-6b7a-43cd-9457-386c90d1a8a4">
      <Text>End of Act Three</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="New Act" id="6b67055e-8e0a-4c01-b26e-48bdef828a9a">
      <Text>Tag</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading" id="203e90d0-b872-482d-9a92-9a2948f0131e">
      <SceneProperties Length="3/8" Page="30" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RIVER">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text Style="Bold+AllCaps">INT. River’s Office - Day</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="d230b23b-6008-4c76-baf8-4b3bccd15e77">
      <Text>On a tablet, one of Ray’s videos from </Text>
      <Text Style="Italic">Plasma with the Facts</Text>
      <Text> YouTube channel is playing.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="d230b23b-6008-4c76-baf8-4b3bccd15e77">
      <Text>River’s fingers scroll to the suggestion panel, featuring Ms. Aurora’s videos. She clicks and lets Ms. Aurora’s video play.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="61007c1e-d262-462b-9951-0f2ec49133b3">
      <Text>At her desk, River shifts from a frown to a smile. She gets out her phone, dials, and puts it to her ear.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character" id="34b94bd8-c6a1-4bbe-a38b-411ba97c8635">
      <Text>River</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="82ec4d5a-6f06-4286-8639-ed7c96642421">
      <Text>Morning. Let’s dismiss auditions, shall we. It’s no longer necessary. I just found our newest host of </Text>
      <Text Style="Italic">StarPower</Text>
      <Text>. Ms. Aurora Starling.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action" id="5f731dab-ad66-4a16-be50-c9e01ae34e3a">
      <Text>Ms. Aurora’s video continues to play.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="End of Act" id="1d686bb2-d1c8-465d-b94b-e6b312d4c003">
      <Text>End of Pilot</Text>
    </Paragraph>
  </Content>

